-for-a-national-cause%2Farticleshow%2F102748849.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20surrounds%2019th%20century%20'vampire'%20found%20buried%20in%20New%20England%20with%20his%20thigh%20bones%20crossed%20over%20his%20chest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20show%20a%20skull%20stained%20by%20time%20next%20to%20the%20picture%20of%20a%20short-haired%20graying%20middle%20aged%20main%20wearing%2019th%20century%20garb.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da02351f51cc001968b423%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESide-by-side%20images%20shows%20the%20skull%20and%20a%20facial%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BConnecticut%20Vampire.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESgt.%20Robert%20Trujillo%20Armed%20Forces%20Medical%20Examiner%20System%3B%20Parabon%20NanoLabs%20and%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20DNA%20Identification%20Laboratory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%2019th%20century%20skeleton%20buried%20in%20an%20unusual%20position%20was%20uncovered%20in%20Connecticut%20in%201990.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20skeleton's%20skull%20and%20limbs%20were%20arranged%20on%20top%20of%20its%20ribs%20in%20a%20skull-and-crossbones%20motif.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EScientists%2C%20who%20reconstructed%20the%20man's%20face%2C%20believe%20that%20he%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20vampire%2C%20but%20others%20aren't%20so%20sure.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20behind%20a%2019th%20century%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-find-vampire-child-padlocked-in-polish-graveyard-2023-8%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bvampire%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20was%20found%20buried%20in%20rural%20Connecticut%20in%201990%20has%20baffled%20scientists%20for%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Barber%20was%20about%2055%20when%20he%20was%20first%20buried%20in%20Griswold%2C%20Connecticut%20in%20the%201800s.%20But%20when%20his%20remains%20were%20uncovered%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20150%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20he%20had%20been%20decapitated%2C%20and%20his%20skull%20and%20thigh%20bones%20had%20been%20placed%20across%20his%20ribcage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looked%20like%20a%20skull-and-crossbones%20motif%2C%20a%20Jolly%20Roger.%20I'd%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Connecticut%20state%20archaeologist%2C%20Nick%20Bellantoni%2C%20told%20the%20Smithsonian%20magazine%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remains%20have%20intrigued%20researchers%20ever%20since.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20DNA%20analysis%20has%20helped%20scientists%20uncover%20the%20tale%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-vampire-skeleton-discovered-in-17th-century-graveyard-poland-2022-9%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bvampire's%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%2C%20however%2C%20still%20can't%20agree%20on%20why%20he%20was%20placed%20in%20such%20an%20unusual%20position.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20skull-and-crossbones%20motif%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20child%20first%20ran%20home%20saying%20he'd%20seen%20a%20skull%20in%20a%20hillside%20gravel%20mine%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20police%20cordoned%20off%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20had%20never%20been%20known%20to%20be%20a%20cemetery%2C%20and%20local%20law%20enforcement%20believed%20the%20remains%20could%20belong%20to%20the%20victim%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2nd-circuit-nominee-hearing-on-hold-2010-3%5C%22%3Elocal%20serial%20killer%20Michael%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Smithsonian%20Magazine%20reported%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20scientists%20quickly%20identified%20the%20bones%20were%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20years%20old.%20The%20site%20contained%2029%20burials%20that%20were%20typical%20of%20the%201700%20and%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20set%20of