h%20genealogy%20research%20restored%20the%20man's%20name%20in%202019%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2073-4425%2F10%2F9%2F636%2Fhtm%5C%22%3EJohn%20Baker%2C%20a%2055-year-old%20man%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20died%20in%20the%20area%20in%201826.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20analysis%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.vcu.edu%2Farticle%2F2023%2F01%2F19th-century-vampire-receives-forensic-facial-reconstruction-from-vcu-researchers%5C%22%3EBaker%20died%20of%20tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20a%20poorly%20understood%20disease%20known%20as%20consumption%20that%20ravaged%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%20was%20likely%20a%20fairly%20modest%20farmer%20in%20life.%20It's%20likely%20that%20it%20was%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMedicalMuseum%2Fvideos%2F2043945279234361%5C%22%3Ein%20his%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20would%20have%20gained%20this%20status%20as%20a%20potential%20%26quot%3Bvampire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuberculosis%20is%20accompanied%20by%20dramatic%20weight%20loss%2C%20graying%20of%20the%20skin%2C%20and%20blood%20being%20coughed%20up%2C%20which%20may%20have%20frightened%20those%20close%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDNA%20analysis%2C%20AI%2C%20and%203D%20scanning%20revealed%20his%20face%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20a%20face%20to%20the%20name%2C%20Virginia-based%20forensic%20DNA%20firm%20Parabon%20NanoLabs%20and%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20DNA%20Identification%20Laboratory%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.einnews.com%2Fpr_news%2F598602717%2F19th-century-new-england-vampire-undergoes-21st-century-dna-analysis%5C%22%3Eteamed%20up%20to%20analyze%20DNA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0extracted%20from%20Barber's%20remains%20%E2%80%94%20or%20what%20was%20left%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20illustrations%20show%20a%20digital%203D%20scan%20of%20the%20Connecticut%20Vampire's%20skull%2C%20nex