ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESushmita%20Sen%20plays%20transgender%20activist%20Gauri%20Sawant%20in%20%3Cem%3ETaali%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20biographical%20drama%20created%20by%20Arjun%20Singh%20Baran%20and%20Kartik%20D.%20Nishandar%20and%20directed%20by%20Ravi%20Jadhav.%20The%20composure%20and%20vigour%20with%20which%20the%20lead%20actor%20slips%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20the%20complex%20character%20is%20worthy%20of%20unstinted%20applause.%20However%2C%20the%20six-episode%20JioCinema%20series%2C%20notwithstanding%20many%20an%20admirable%20element%2C%20is%20strangely%20inert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20pieces%20together%20the%20key%20turning%20points%20of%20Gauri%20Sawant's%20eventful%20life%2C%20her%20estrangement%20from%20her%20policeman-father%20(played%20splendidly%20by%20Nandu%20Madhav)%20being%20the%20most%20emotionally%20wrenching%20of%20them.%20She%20has%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20her%20physiological%20and%20emotional%20confusions%20as%20she%20grows%20up%20in%20a%20conservative%20environment%20that%20makes%20the%20process%20all%20that%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Gauri%20evolves%20from%20a%20girl%20trapped%20in%20a%20boy's%20body%20craving%20acceptance%20into%20an%20assertive%20transwoman%20to%20files%20a%20petition%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20recognition%20of%20her%20community%20as%20the%20third%20gender%2C%20she%20has%20to%20take%20on%20inimical%20forces%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20world%20of%20transgenders.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20pimps%20and%20brothel-keepers.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20self-appointed%20guardians%20or%20orthodoxy%20and%20people%20in%20positions%20of%20power%20(one%20such%20person%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20played%20by%20Ananth%20Mahadevan%2C%20faces%20the%20brunt%20of%20her%20aggression)%20stand%20in%20her%20way.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgBFczsrs0_c%3Fsi%3D5gS_IbFz4LWRitUc%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20ample%20drama%20inherent%20in%20Gauri's%20journey%20towards%20asserting%20her%20gender%20identity.%20She%20makes%20both%20friends%20and%20enemies.%20As%20her%20network%20expands%20and%20her%20fame%20spreads%2C%20she%20gravitates%20towards%20activism%20aimed%20at%20securing%20the%20legal%20rights%20of%20transgenders.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20the%20Gauri%20Sawant%20story%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20The%20retelling%20does%20not%20feel%20unnecessary%20because%20Taali%20serves%20the%20purpose%20of%20furthering%20awareness%20about%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20third%20gender%20and%20dispelling%20misconceptions%20that%20have%20prevented%20society%20them%20with%20the%20respect%20that%20they%20deserve%20as%20citizens%20of%20a%20free%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20narrative%20meat%2C%20there%20is%20enough%20in%20%3Cem%3ETaali%3C%2Fem%3E%20sustain%20the%20six%20episodes%2C%20but%20where%20the%20script%20fails%20a%20tad%20in%20in%20not%20attempting%20a%20proper%20deep%20dive%20into%20the%20world%20that%20the%20transgender%20community%20inhabits%20and%20apprising%20the%20audience%20of%20those%20aspects%20of%20their%20lives%20that%20are%20not%20already%20known%20(often%20in%20distorted%20ways)%20or%20fully%20appreciated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20they%20are%20sexually%20exploited%2C%20mistreated%20by%20the%20police%20and%20others%20arms%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20live%20with%20the%20'stigma'%20of%20being%20different.%20A%20little%20detailing%20regarding%20their%20inner%20compulsions%20and%20the%20minutiae%20of%20Gauri%20Sawant's%20personal%20and%20public%20battle%20to%20bring%20people%20like%20her%20on%20even%20keel%20with%20the%20nation's%20binary%20population%20would%20have%20lent%20the%20series%20far%20greater%20potency.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20both%20the%20lead%20and%20the%20director%2C%20working%20with%20a%20script%20by%20Kshitij%20Patwardhan%2C%20eschew%20exaggeration%20or%20any%20form%20of%20sensationalism%20in%20bringing%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20war%20that%20Gauri%20Sawant%20had%20to%20wage%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20community%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins.%20The%20restraint%20works%20to%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20series%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3ETaali%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20pierces%20past%20the%20obvious%20facets%20of%20the%20protagonist's%20struggles%20with%20herself%2C%20her%20family%2C%20her%20society%2C%20her%20community%20and%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20land.%20The%20series%20deals%20with%20the%20broad%20themes%20the%20surround%20the%20reality%20of%20being%20different%20in%20a%20milieu%20in%20which%20normality%20is%20defined%20by%20the%20cis%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20that%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20asked%20about%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETaali%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%3A%20would%20it%20not%20have%20been%20better%20had%20the%20central%20role%20been%20played%20by%20a%20real-life%20transgender%20actor%3F%20Not%20that%20Susmita%20Sen%20is%20out%20of%20place%20-%20she%20rustles%20up%20a%20convincing%20portrait%20of%20an%20individual%20who%20went%20in%20for%20a%20sex%20change%20operation%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20still%20a%20very%20rare%20procedure%20in%20India%20and%20then%20proceeded%20to%20become%20the%20voice%20of%20all%20transgenders.%20But%20no%20matter%20how%20good%20she%20is%20as%20Gauri%20Sawant%2C%20absolute%20authenticity%20is%20a%20tough%20ask%20here.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20episode%20of%20%3Cem%3ETaali%3C%2Fem%3E%20plays%20out%20for%20the%20most%20part%20outside%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20where%20Gauri's%20petition%20is%20about%20to%20come%20up%20for%20hearing.%20The%20narrative%20moves%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20the%20present%20and%20her%20difficult%20childhood%20as%20the%20show%20seeks%20create%20a%20rounded%20portrait%20of%20a%20remarkable%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20narration%20flows%20out%20of%20a%20conversation%20that%20Gauri%20has%20with%20a%20journalist%20(Maya%20Rachel%20McManus)%20-%20a%20framing%20device%20that%20leads%20into%20a%20series%20of%20flashbacks%20that%20reveal%20the%20Ganesh-to-Gauri%20transformation.%20At%20school.%20a%20teacher%20asks%20Ganesh%20what%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20life.%20The%20boy%20replies%3A%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%20The%20teacher%20shuts%20him%20up.%20Boys%20can't%20be%20mothers%2C%20she%20says.%20Ganesh's%20desire%20to%20be%20a%20mother%20one%20day%20becomes%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20evolution%20of%20her%20persona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20crucial%20scene%2C%20a%20transgender%20woman%2C%20Nargis%20(Sheetal%20Kale)%2C%20walks%20out%20in%20a%20huff%20from%20a%20meeting%20convened%20by%20a%20gay%20rights%20activist%20(Ankur%20Bhatia)%20because%20Ganesh%2FGauri%20isn't%20really%20like%20them.%20Change%20yourself%20not%20just%20on%20the%20outside%20but%20also%20from%20within%2C%20Nargis%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20sets%20Ganesh%20thinking.%20It%20compels%20him%20to%20look%20at%20himself%20in%20a%20different%20light%20and%20take%20the%20next%20logical%20steps%20to%20reinvent%20himself%20physically.%20A%20handful%20of%20scenes%20are%20devoted%20to%20the%20transformation%2C%20but%20the%20series%20views%20the%20gender%20transition%20from%20an%20objective%20distance%20rather%20than%20delve%20into%20the%20deeper%20psychological%20dimensions%20of%20it.%20That%20prevents%20Taali%20from%20being%20the%20resounding%20series%20that%20it%20could%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20Ravi%20Jadhav%2C%20that%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20surprise.%20The%20director%20has%20a%20track%20record%20of%20creating%20outliers%20who%20fearlessly%20take%20on%20social%2