smashed%20Earth's%20previous%20July%20record%20by%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20a%20degree%20Fahrenheit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20July%202023%20was%200.24%C2%B0C%20warmer%20than%20any%20other%20July%20in%20NASA's%20record%2C%20and%20it%20was%201.18%C2%B0C%20warmer%20than%20the%20average%20July%20between%201951%20and%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E(1%20of%205)%20IT'S%20OFFICIAL%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEarth%20just%20had%20its%20hottest%20July%20in%20174%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4th%20consecutive%20month%20of%20record-high%20global%20ocean%20surface%20temperature.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAntarctica%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSeaIce%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SeaIce%3C%2Fa%3E%20coverage%20had%20a%20record-low%20in%20July%20for%20the%203rd%20consecutive%20month.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlRgypbiSed%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlRgypbiSed%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNOAANCEI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40NOAANCEI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FStateOfClimate%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23StateOfClimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn1ud8u87x2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fn1ud8u87x2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NOAA%20(%40NOAA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNOAA%2Fstatus%2F1691099763167666176%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''NASA%20data%20confirms%20what%20billions%20around%20the%20world%20literally%20felt%3A%20temperatures%20in%20July%202023%20made%20it%20the%20hottest%20month%20on%20record.%20In%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Americans%20are%20right%20now%20experiencing%20firsthand%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20underscoring%20the%20urgency%20of%20President%20Biden's%20historic%20climate%20agenda%2C''%C2%A0said%20NASA%20Administrator%20Bill%20Nelson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20must%20act%20now%20to%20protect%20our%20communities%20and%20planet%3B%20it's%20the%20only%20one%20we%20have%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20South%20America%2C%20North%20Africa%2C%20North%20America%2C%20and%20the%20Antarctic%20Peninsula%20were%20especially%20hot%2C%20experiencing%20temperatures%20increasing%20around%204%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20average.%20NASA's%20analysis%20also%20showed%20especially%20warm%20ocean%20temperatures%20in%20the%20eastern%20tropical%20Pacific%2C%20evidence%20of%20the%20El%20Nino%20that%20began%20developing%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavin%20Schmidt%2C%20director%20of%20the%20NASA%20Goddard%20Institute%20for%20Space%20Studies%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20the%20biggest%20impacts%20of%20El%20Nino%20will%20likely%20occur%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20July%20was%20not%20just%20warmer%20than%20any%20previous%20July%20-%20it%20was%20the%20warmest%20month%20in%20our%20record%2C%20which%20goes%20back%20to%201880.%20The%20science%20is%20clear%20this%20isn't%20normal.%20Alarming%20warming%20around%20the%20world%20is%20driven%20primarily%20by%20human-caused%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%20And%20that%20rise%20in%20average%20temperatures%20is%20fueling%20dangerous%20extreme%20heat%20that%20people%20are%20experiencing%20here%20at%20home%20and%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Schmidt%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20back%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjuly-hottest-month-ever-recorded-climate-watchdog-issues-warning-4279664%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Union's%20climate%20observatory%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20confirmed%20that%20July%20was%20the%20hottest%20month%20ever%20recorded%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NASA%20data%2C%20the%20five%20hottest%20Julys%20since%201880%20have%20all%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692099120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fsmm1o6_heatwave-heat-wave-ani_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-confirms-july-2023-as-the-hottest-month-ever-says-we-must-act-now-4300074%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overall%2C%20July%202023%20was%200.24C%20warmer%20than%20any%20other%20July%20in%20NASA's%20record%2C%20and%20it%20was%201.18C%20warmer%20than%20the%20average%20July%20between%201951%20and%201980.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-confirms-july-2023-as-the-hottest-month-ever-says-we-must-act-now-4300074%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-confirms-july-2023-as-the-hottest-month-ever-says-we-must-act-now-4300074%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-confirms-july-2023-as-the-hottest-month-ever-says-we-must-act-now-4300074%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Demon%20Demographics%2C%20Nazi%20Germany%20and%20the%20Making%20of%20Racialised%20Anxiety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15155116%2FLebensborn-III.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDemon%20demographics%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Ethey%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20breeding%20faster%20than%20%3Cem%3Eus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ewe%3C%2Fem%3E%20need%20more%20numbers%20%E2%80%93%20have%20always%20served%20the%20cause%20of%20totalitarianism%2C%20racism%20and%20the%20genocidal%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENazi%20Germany%20exemplified%20how%20such%20a%20demon%20demographics%20enabled%20the%20making%20of%20a%20nationwide%2C%20racialised%20anxiety%20around%20the%20need%20for%20greater%20numbers%20of%20the%20Aryan%20race%20so%20that%20the%20Third%20Reich%20would%20last%20a%20thousand%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20demon%20demographics%20generated%20a%20plan%20for%20appropriate%20breeding%20and%20training%2C%20and%20the%20incorporation%20of%20sexuality%2C%20maternity%20and%20childhood%20into%20a%20national%20project.%20Some%20accounts%20by%20the%20children%20of%20this%20project%20have%20surfaced%20recently%2C%20whose%20texts%20read%20like%20a%20cross%20between%20a%20detective%20thriller%20and%20a%20horror%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20moving%20account%20of%20her%20childhood%20and%20an%20adult%20life%20spent%20seeking%20her%20biological%20parents%2C%20Ingrid%20von%20Oelhafen%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FHitler_s_Forgotten_Children%2Fq2MXswEACAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHitler%E2%80%99s%20Forgotten%20Children%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20records%20how%20she%20was%20mystified%20by%20some%20family%20documents%20which%20listed%20her%20name%20as%20%E2%80%98Erika%20Matko%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuzzled%2C%20von%20Oelhafen%20traverses%20archives%2C%20meets%20people%2C%20and%20pursues%20vague%20leads%20to%20trace%20the%20story%20of%20her%20birth.%20One%20puzzling%20document%20she%20unearths%20is%20a%20receipt%20that%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20Hermann%20von%20Oelhafen%2C%20of%20Gentz%20Strasse%205%2C%20Munich%2C%20has%20on%203%20June%201944%2C%20taken%20into%20their%20home%20the%20ethnic%20German%20girl%20Erika%20Matkow%20%5Bsic%5D%2C%20born%2011%20November%201941.%20Because%20she%20is%20a%20child%20of%20German%20stock%2C%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Reichsfuhrer%20she%20is%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20German%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20discovers%20accurate%20information%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLilienthal%E2%80%99s%20research%20had%20found%20the%20name%20Erika%20Matko%20in%20some%20long-forgotten%20records%20%E2%80%A6%20She%20had%20been%20raised%20in%20one%20of%20its%20children%E2%80%99s%20homes%3A%20a%20place%20called%20Sonnenweise%20%E2%80%A6%20at%20Kohren-Sahlis.%20Since%20I%20was%20%E2%80%93%20or%20once%20had%20been%20%E2%80%93%20Erika%20Matko%2C%20that%20meant%20I%20was%20a%20Lebensborn%20baby%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErika%20Matko%2FIngrid%20von%20Oelhafen%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20baby.%20The%20discovery%20inverts%20her%20sense%20of%20self%2C%20because%20she%20had%20lived%20under%20another%2C%20assumed%20identity%20all%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%98Fount%20or%20Fountain%20of%20Life%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20a%20Nazi%20organisation%20whose%20purpose%20was%20ostensibly%20to%20take%20care%20of%20expectant%20mothers%2C%20including%20unwed%20ones%2C%20who%20would%20produce%20healthy%20Aryan%20children%20to%20populate%20the%20Third%20Reich.%20Its%20principal%20officers%2C%20Gregor%20Ebner%2C%20Max%20Sollmann%20and%20others%20were%20prosecuted%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fencyclopedia.ushmm.org%2Fcontent%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fsubsequent-nuremberg-proceedings-case-8-the-rusha-case%5C%22%3ECase%208%20of%20the%20Subsequent%20Nuremberg%20Trials%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20but%20not%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-to-indict-persecutors%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Indict%20Perpetrators%20%E2%80%93%20Nuremberg%E2%80%99s%20History%20Lessons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20monitored%20directly%20by%20Heinrich%20Himmler%2C%20who%20even%20drew%20up%20dietary%20charts%20for%20expectant%20mothers.%20This%20organisation%2C%20the%20proverbial%20tip%20of%20the%20eugenics%20iceberg%2C%20had%20its%20origins%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98fear%20of%20small%20numbers%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20adapt%20Arjun%20Appadurai%E2%80%99s%20resonant%20phrase%3A%20the%20Nazi%20fear%20that%20the%20Aryan%20population%20was%20on%20the%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fragmented%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20records%20are%20fascinating%20for%20what%20they%20reveal%20about%20theories%20of%20racial%20purity%2C%20the%20discourse%20of%20demographic%20decline%20and%20the%20exhortation%20to%20produce%20more%20numbers%20of%20a%20specific%20race%20in%20order%20to%20dominate%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98fear%20of%20small%20numbers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20World%20War%20I%2C%20Germany%20had%20the%20sharpest%20birth-rate%20decline%20in%20Europe.%20In%201900%2C%20the%20statistics%20showed%20an%20average%20rate%20of%20births%20per%20thousand%20of%2035.8%2C%20but%20by%201932%2C%20it%20was%20down%20to%2014.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20population%20of%2037%20million%20in%201885%20had%20produced%20the%20same%20number%20of%20children%20as%20the%20population%20of%2067%20million%20in%201935!%20Of%20the%2016%20million%20married%20women%20at%20the%20end%20of%201938%2C%2022%25%20were%20childless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20chosen%20race%20of%20Aryans%20simply%20did%20not%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20create%20and%20sustain%20the%20Third%20Reich%20became%20a%20matter%20of%20considerable%20concern%20for%20Hitler%2C%20Himmler%20and%20the%20SS.%20In%201936%2C%20Himmler%20sent%20out%20a%20circular%20that%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SS%20has%20taken%20a%20first%20step%20in%20issuing%20the%20marriage%20order.%20But%20a%20marriage%20without%20many%20children%20is%20no%20more%20than%20an%20affair.%20I%20hope%20here%20too%20members%20of%20the%20SS%2C%20and%20particularly%20its%20leaders%2C%20will%20set%20a%20good%20example.%20Four%20children%20are%20the%20necessary%20minimum%20for%20a%20good%20and%20healthy%20marriage%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20entry%20into%20Poland%20marking%20the%20start%20of%20World%20War%20II%2C%20Himmler%20issued%20a%20circular%20on%20October%2028%2C%201939%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20war%20involves%20a%20tremendous%20letting%20of%20the%20best%20blood.%20Many%20victories%20won%20by%20the%20force%20of%20arms%20have%20been%20a%20shattering%20defeat%20for%20a%20nation%E2%80%99s%20vitality%20and%20blood.%20But%20the%20sadly%20necessary%20death%20of%20the%20best%20men%2C%20deplorable%20though%20it%20is%2C%20is%20not%20the%20worst.%20Far%20worse%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20children%20who%20were%20not%20born%20of%20the%20living%20during%20the%20war%20and%20of%20the%20dead%20after%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Rudolf%20Hess%20published%20%E2%80%98An%20Open%20Letter%20to%20an%20Unmarried%20Mother%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20which%20he%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20wartime%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20death%20of%20many%20of%20our%20best%20men%2C%20every%20new%20life%20is%20of%20special%20importance%20to%20the%20nation.%20Hence%2C%20if%20racially%20unobjectionable%20young%20men%20going%20on%20active%20service%20leave%20behind%20children%20who%20pass%20on%20their%20blood%20to%20future%20generations%20through%20a%20girl%20of%20the%20right%20age%20and%20similar%20healthy%20heredity%20%E2%80%A6%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20preserve%20this%20valuable%20national%20wealth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%2C%20then%2C%20a%20matter%20of%20numbers%3A%20the%20Teutons%20had%20to%20be%20in%20a%20majority%20so%20that%20any%20and%20every%20threat%20to%20the%20nation%20could%20be%20thwarted.%20The%20Third%20Reich%E2%80%99s%20future%20depended%20on%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20incentives%20to%20encourage%20the%20reproduction%20of%20the%20preferred%20race%20included%3A%20every%20year%20on%20the%20birthday%20of%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20fertile%20women%20were%20awarded%20the%20Honour%20Cross%20of%20the%20German%20Mother.%20Women%20who%20had%20had%20more%20than%20four%20children%20were%20given%20a%20bronze%20medal%3B%20those%20with%20more%20than%20six%20earned%20silver%3B%20and%20those%20with%20more%20than%20eight%2C%20a%20gold%20medal.%20As%20a%20Nazi%20mouthpiece%20put%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20many%20children%20is%20the%20real%20meaning%20of%20life.%20That%20is%20why%20a%20man%20who%20has%20become%20the%20father%20of%20healthy%20children%20is%20worth%20more%20to%20us%20than%20all%20the%20deliberately%20childless%20priests%20of%20a%20whole%20millennium.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20German%20woman%20who%20has%20given%20life%20to%20many%20children%20and%20has%20looked%20after%20them%20for%20a%20lifetime%20is%20to%20us%20a%20phenomenon%20more%20sacred%20than%20all%20the%20childless%20nuns%20our%20nation%20has%20ever%20produced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimmler%20often%20used%20the%20following%20analogy%20to%20support%20larger%20numbers%20of%20progeny%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSupposing%20Bach%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20after%20her%20fifth%20or%20sixth%20or%20even%20twelfth%20child%2C%20had%20said%20that%E2%80%99ll%20do%2C%20enough%20is%20enough%2C%20the%20works%20of%20Bach%20would%20never%20have%20been%20written.%20The%20same%20applies%20to%20Richard%20Wagner.%20He%20was%20a%20sixth%20child.%20I%20tell%20you%20our%20culture%20would%20have%20been%20tremendously%20impoverished%20if%20in%20the%20old%20days%2C%20families%20had%20generally%20been%20limited%20to%20four%20or%20five%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o-300x215.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668224%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENazi%20policy%20encouraged%20racially%20%E2%80%98acceptable%E2%80%99%20couples%20to%20have%20as%20many%20children%20as%20possible.%20Pictured%20here%20is%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20family.%20Photo%3A%20Dan%20Iggers%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY-NC%20SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreeding%20%3Cem%3Efor%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Fuhrer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20camps%2C%20fifteen%20of%20them%20in%201943%2C%20were%20the%20place%2C%20in%20Nazi%20fantasy%2C%20where%20the%20Teutonic%20race%20would%20be%20nurtured%2C%20and%20who%20would%20all%20be%2C%20in%20a%20description%20by%20the%20Nazi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20official%20theorist%20Hans%20Gunther%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CTall%2C%20long%20head%2C%20narrow%20face%2C%20well-defined%20chin%2C%20narrow%20nose%20with%20very%20high%20root%2C%20soft%20fair%20(golden-blond)%20hair%2C%20receding%20light%20(blue%20or%20grey)%20eyes%2C%20pink%20white%20skin%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20magnificent%20specimens%20of%20the%20Teutonic%20race%20were%20contrasted%20with%20other%20races%2C%20what%20the%20Main%20Race%20and%20Settlement%20Office%20(RuSHA%2C%20established%20in%201931)%20in%20a%201942%20pamphlet%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Sub-human%E2%80%99%20described%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sub-human%2C%20that%20biologically%20seemingly%20complete%20similar%20creation%20of%20nature%20with%20hands%2C%20feet%20and%20a%20kind%20of%20brain%2C%20with%20eyes%20and%20a%20mouth%2C%20is%20nevertheless%20a%20completely%20different%2C%20dreadful%20creature.%20He%20is%20only%20a%20rough%20copy%20of%20a%20human%20being%2C%20with%20human-%20like%20facial%20traits%20but%20nonetheless%20morally%20and%20mentally%20lower%20than%20any%20animal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20this%20creature%20there%20is%20a%20fearful%20chaos%20of%20wild%2C%20uninhibited%20passions%2C%20nameless%20destructiveness%2C%20the%20most%20primitive%20desires%2C%20the%20nakedest%20vulgarity.%20Sub-human%2C%20otherwise%20nothing.%20For%20all%20that%20bear%20a%20human%20face%20are%20not%20equal.%20Woe%20to%20him%20who%20forgets%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20as%201935%2C%20the%20Nazi%20youth%20movement%20proposed%20%E2%80%98biological%20marriages%E2%80%99%20to%20give%20respectability%20to%20extramarital%20sexual%20relations%20between%20young%20people%20who%20shared%20the%20Nazi%20vision.%20Nazi%20youth%20camps%20indoctrinated%20the%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20particularly%20the%20latter%2C%20of%20their%20duty%20to%20reproduce.%20As%20Marc%20Hillel%20and%20Clarissa%20Henry%20in%20%3Cem%3EChildren%20of%20the%20SS%3C%2Fem%3E%20put%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNazi%20character%20training%20and%20the%20sexual%20education%20that%20went%20with%20it%20thus%20largely%20took%20place%20at%20the%20camps%2C%20outings%20and%20sporting%2C%20and%20quasi-military%20meetings%20to%20which%20the%20regime%20attached%20so%20much%20importance.%20Children%20no%20longer%20belonged%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20to%20the%20Nazi%20movement.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20Nazi%20Party%20published%20in%20January%201921%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20they%20undertook%20to%20exclude%20women%20permanently%20from%20important%20posts%20in%20political%20life.%20Their%20role%20in%20national%20politics%20and%20life%20was%20made%20clear%3A%20the%20kitchen%2C%20the%20church%2C%20children.%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20stated%20it%20simply%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20woman%E2%80%99s%20duty%20is%20to%20be%20attractive%20and%20bear%20children.%20The%20idea%20is%20not%20as%20vulgar%20and%20old-fashioned%20as%20it%20might%20seem.%20A%20female%20bird%20makes%20itself%20beautiful%20for%20its%20mate%20and%20hatches%20out%20her%20eggs%20for%20him.%20The%20removal%20of%20women%20from%20public%20life%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20only%20to%20restore%20their%20female%20dignity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Genders%20of%20Atrocity%3A%20Before%20Lynndie%20England%20There%20Was%20Ilse%20Koch%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgender%2Fgenders-of-atrocity-before-lynndie-england-there-was-ilse-koch%5C%22%3EGenders%20of%20Atrocity%3A%20Before%20Lynndie%20England%20There%20Was%20Ilse%20Koch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20dignity%20must%20not%20deter%20the%20women%20from%20actively%20increasing%20the%20numbers%20for%20the%20Third%20Reich.%20Himmler%E2%80%99s%20order%20%E2%80%98for%20the%20whole%20SS%20police%20forces%E2%80%99%20of%20October%2028%2C%201939%20appears%20in%20an%20English%20translation%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FThe_Tragedy_of_Children_Under_Nazi_Rule%2F7F1KAAAAIAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EKiryl%20Sosnowski%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tragedy%20of%20Children%20Under%20Nazi%20Rule%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1962)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNotwithstanding%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20perhaps%20once%20necessary%20bourgeoise%20laws%20and%20customs%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20task%20for%20German%20women%20and%20girls%20of%20good%20blood%2C%20also%20outside%20matrimony%2C%20to%20become%2C%20not%20out%20of%20levity%20but%20out%20of%20a%20feeling%20of%20responsibility%2C%20the%20deepest%20and%20earnest%20moral%20conviction%2C%20the%20mothers%20of%20children%20begotten%20by%20soldiers%20going%20to%20the%20front%2C%20about%20whom%20only%20fate%20knows%20whether%20they%20will%20return%20home%20or%20fall%20for%20Germany.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirls%20from%20as%20early%20as%201935%20were%20cultured%20into%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20reproduce%20%3Cem%3Efor%20the%20Fuhrer%20and%20the%20Fatherland%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Reproduction%20was%20a%20moral%20and%20national%20duty%2C%20as%20one%20circular%2C%20obviously%20directed%20at%20German%20girls%2C%20of%20the%20youth%20movement%20described%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20shall%20all%20today%20or%20tomorrow%20be%20able%20to%20abandon%20ourselves%20to%20the%20rich%20emotional%20experience%20of%20procreating%20in%20the%20company%20of%20a%20healthy%20young%20man%2C%20without%20troubling%20about%20the%20impediments%20that%20encumber%20the%20antiquated%20institution%20of%20marriage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20breeding%20and%20kidnapping%20for%20the%20Fuhrer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuSHA%20approval%20was%20required%20for%20SS%20personnel%20to%20marry%2C%20and%20the%20approval%20was%20contingent%20upon%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20proving%20their%20racial%20purity%20and%20suitability%20for%20breeding.%20In%201935%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20project%20was%20formally%20launched%20under%20RuSHA.%20The%20order%20launching%20the%20organisation%20stated%20as%20its%20objectives%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20To%20support%20racially%20and%20genetically%20valuable%20large%20families.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20To%20accommodate%20and%20look%20after%20racially%20and%20genetically%20valuable%20expectant%20mothers%20who%2C%20after%20careful%20investigation%20of%20their%20families%20and%20those%20of%20the%20fathers%20of%20their%20children%20by%20RuSHA%2C%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20equally%20valuable%20children.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20look%20after%20those%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20To%20look%20after%20the%20mothers%20of%20those%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%201939%20orders%20from%20Himmler%20outlined%20the%20plan%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20All%20children%20of%20good%20blood%2C%20whether%20born%20in%20or%20out%20of%20marriage%2C%20whose%20fathers%20have%20died%20in%20the%20war%2C%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20guardianship%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Reichsfuhrer-SS%20by%20special%20officers%2C%20appointed%20by%20me%20personally.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20will%20contact%20these%20mothers%20and%20will%20take%20over%20care%20for%20the%20material%20and%20spiritual%20welfare%20of%20their%20children%20until%20their%20maturity%2C%20so%20that%20no%20mother%20or%20widow%20could%20find%20herself%20in%20distress%20or%20need.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20The%20Schutzstaffel%20%5BSS%5D%20will%20take%20care%2C%20in%20case%20of%20want%20and%20distress%2C%20of%20all%20children%20born%20during%20the%20war%2C%20whether%20in%20or%20out%20of%20marriage%2C%20and%20of%20the%20mothers%20to%20be.%20When%20the%20fathers%20return%20after%20the%20war%2C%20the%20Schutzstaffel%20will%20secure%20for%20them%20additional%20economic%20aid%20on%20an%20extensive%20scale%2C%20on%20individual%20or%20substantiated%20application.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E3.%20SS-men%20and%20you%2C%20mothers%20of%20the%20children%20awaited%20by%20Germany%2C%20show%20that%20because%20or%20your%20faith%20in%20the%20Fuhrer%20and%20because%20of%20your%20desire%20for%20the%20eternal%20life%20of%20our%20blood%20and%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20give%20new%20life%20for%20Germany%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20you%20know%20how%20to%20bravely%20fight%20and%20die%20for%20Germany.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20to%20be%20absolute%20confidentiality%20over%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20biological%20mother%20%E2%80%93%20photographing%20mothers%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20forbidden%20for%20this%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20and%20foster%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20June%201939%20circular%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20possible%20to%20maintain%20secrecy%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20illegitimate%20children%20born%20in%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20homes%20for%20an%20unlimited%20period.%20The%20Reich%20office%20will%20provide%20a%20certificate%20confirming%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20Aryan%20descent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-1024x666.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-1024x666.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-300x195.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668225%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22546%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKidnapping%20of%20Polish%20children%20during%20a%20Nazi-German%20resettlement%20operation.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20much%20rumour-mongering%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20camps%20served%20as%20brothels%20and%20stud%20farms%20for%20SS%20officers.%20Indeed%2C%20Peter%20Neumann%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FThe_Black_March%2FWy0DAAAAMAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Black%20March%3A%20The%20Personal%20Story%20of%20an%20SS%20Man%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0narrates%20an%20incident%20where%2C%20having%20been%20identified%20as%20%E2%80%98of%20pure%20Aryan%20stock%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20doctor%20tells%20him%20of%20future%20plans%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%E2%80%99ve%20heard%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%2C%20of%20the%20Lebensborn.%20You%20have%20been%20selected%20with%20five%20of%20your%20comrades%20to%20go%20to%20Westphalia.%20Our%20Fuhrer%2C%20having%20been%20advised%20by%20Rosenberg%20and%20Darre%2C%20started%20these%20establishments%2C%20in%20which%20is%20being%20produced%20for%20Germany%20that%20pure%2C%20regenerative%20blood%20which%20we%20need%20so%20badly%20for%20the%20future.%20We%20require%20young%20men%20like%20yourself%2C%20healthy%2C%20intelligent%2C%20tried-and-tested%20Nazis.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20reaches%20one%20such%20camp%2C%20he%20asks%20a%20young%20woman%20about%20the%20place.%20Coquettishly%2C%20she%20responds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98But%20you%E2%80%99re%20dying%20to%20know%20how%20we%20all%20go%20to%20bed%20together%20according%20to%20National%20Socialist%20regulations%3F%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%A6%20A%20strange%20thing%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20country%20to%20ask%20of%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20later%2C%20she%20says%2C%20in%20Neumann%E2%80%99s%20reportage%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Your%20baby-making%20machine%20is%20at%20your%20disposal%E2%80%99.%20Her%20laugh%20sounded%20false.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20pretty%20horrible%2C%20this%20business%20of%20selling%20one%E2%80%99s%20body%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20procreation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%20Neumann%20leaves%2C%20and%20thus%20ends%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cour%20artificial%20love%20affair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20the%20incentives%20and%20facilities%20(such%20as%20the%20camps%20Neumann%20experienced)%20and%20threats%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20for%20the%20SS%20and%20Nazi%20officials%20did%20not%20produce%20the%20expected%20results.%20As%20Larry%20Thompson%E2%80%99s%201971%20essay%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fcentral-european-history%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Flebensborn-and-the-eugenics-policy-of-the-reichsfuhrerss%2F45858920D4BF64CAD2DC33A5D8DB8655%5C%22%3ELebensborn%20and%20the%20Eugenics%20Policy%20of%20the%20Reichsfu%CC%88hrer-SS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20notes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SS%20as%20a%20whole%20failed%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20exhortations%20of%20Himmler%20and%20other%20ideologues%20to%20produce%20more%20children.%20In%20fact%2C%2061%25%20of%20SS%20were%20bachelors%20in%201939%2C%20while%20the%20married%20contingent%20%E2%80%93%20some%2093%2C%20000%20men%20%E2%80%93%20could%20muster%20little%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20children%2C%20or%201.1%20children%20per%20family%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201943%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20future%20rulers%20of%20Europe%2Fthe%20world%20would%20not%20be%20adequate.%20Campaigns%2C%20therefore%2C%20began%20to%20capture%20the%20illegitimate%20offspring%20of%20German%20fathers%20in%20occupied%20territories%20in%20eastern%20and%20southeastern%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Himmler%20authorised%20securing%20the%20children%20of%20%E2%80%98racially%20valuable%E2%80%99%20parents%20across%20the%20occupied%20areas.%20They%20would%20be%20placed%2C%20if%20they%20were%20deemed%20to%20be%20suitably%20Aryan%2C%20in%20German%20foster%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimmler%2C%20always%20a%20person%20who%20could%20draft%20a%20note%20well%2C%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20make%20this%20grand%20Germanisation%20process%20official%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20cases%20when%20foreign%20women%20bear%20children%20of%20German%20men%2C%20the%20same%20should%20happen%20as%20in%20the%20East.%20Mothers%20and%20children%20should%20be%20registered%20by%20us%20and%20brought%20to%20Germany%20or%20made%20to%20stay%20there%20in%20all%20cases%20when%20they%20are%20considered%20racially%20valuable.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20case%20I%20also%20recommend%20the%20establishing%20of%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20home%20for%20children%20of%20foreign%20women%20and%20German%20fathers%2C%20who%20should%20be%20brought%20up%20as%20Germans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20he%20popularised%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98racially%20valuable%20children%E2%80%99%2C%20exhorting%20the%20SS%20and%20others%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMake%20an%20effort%20to%20exclude%20the%20racially%20valuable%20children%20from%20the%20transfer%20and%20to%20send%20them%20to%20the%20old%20Reich%20for%20them%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20in%20special%20educational%20establishments%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20will%20receive%20German%20names%2C%20the%20root%20of%20which%20should%20also%20be%20purely%20German.%20Proof%20of%20their%20origin%20will%20be%20established%20by%20a%20special%20office.%20All%20racially%20valuable%20children%2C%20whose%20parents%20have%20died%20during%20the%20war%20or%20later%20are%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20German%20orphanages%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20brought%20into%20German%20homes%20from%20Poland%20and%20other%20conquered%20territories%20were%20%E2%80%98Germanised%E2%80%99.%20This%20involved%20a%20ceremony%2C%20described%20by%20one%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20staff%20member%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20always%20a%20naming%20ceremony%2C%20and%20an%20official%20from%20the%20register%20office%20was%20always%20there%2C%20and%20the%20mothers%20put%20on%20their%20best%20clothes%20and%20smartened%20up%20the%20children%2C%20and%20the%20living-room%20%E2%80%93%20the%20day%20room%20%E2%80%93%20was%20decorated%20with%20flowers%2C%20and%20it%20was%20all%20very%20solemn%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22797%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony.jpg%20797w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony-300x182.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20such%20naming%20ceremony%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20western%20Germany.%20Photo%3A%20Bundesarchiv%2C%20Bild%20146-1969-062A-58%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC-BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20by%20one%20each%20baby%20was%20given%20its%20name%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20it%20was%20always%20a%20very%20enjoyable%20afternoon%2C%20with%20coffee%20and%20cakes%2C%20and%20it%20was%20really%20very%20nice%20indeed%2C%20with%20the%20gramophone%20records%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20it%20was%20always%20most%20enjoyable.%20Yes%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20call%20it%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20was%20an%20SS%20ceremony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20were%20the%20property%2C%20then%2C%20of%20the%20state.%20Sex%20was%20for%20procreation%2C%20geared%20towards%20increasing%20the%20numerical%20superiority%20of%20the%20Aryans.%20Kidnapping%2C%20re-culturation%20and%20reproductive%20totalitarianism%20were%20all%20grist%20to%20the%20Nazi%20mill%20because%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftile.loc.gov%2Fstorage-services%2Fservice%2Fll%2Fllmlp%2FNT_Indictments%2FNT_Indictments.pdf%5C%22%3ENuremberg%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20RuSHA%20officials%20noted%20that%20among%20their%20crimes%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20transfer%20of%20populations%2C%20Germanisation%20of%20citizens%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20deportation%20of%20Eastern%20workers%2C%20deportation%20to%20slave%20labour%20of%20members%20of%20other%20countries%20eligible%20for%20Ger%C2%ADmanisation%2C%20kidnapping%20of%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cracially%20valuable%E2%80%9D%20children%20for%20Germanisation%2C%20participation%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20abortions%20on%20Eastern%20workers%2C%20murder%20and%20plunder%20of%20property.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20listed%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20acts%20of%20%E2%80%98kidnapping%20of%20foreign%20children%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20Germanisation%E2%80%99%20and%20describes%20how%20%E2%80%9Cnumerous%20Czech%2C%20Polish%2C%20Yugoslav%20and%20Norwegian%20children%20were%20taken%20from%20their%20parents%20or%20guardians%20and%20classified%20according%20to%20their%20%E2%80%98racial%20value%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExhortations%20to%20certain%20communities%20to%20breed%20because%20they%20will%20otherwise%20be%20overrun%20by%20other%20communities%20is%20a%20political%20plank%20that%20marks%20the%20beginnings%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emphasis%20on%20purity%20%E2%80%93%20and%20proscription%20of%20mixed%20faith%20and%20mixed%20community%20liaisons%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20a%20preliminary%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20the%20purity%20of%20nations%2C%20communities%20and%20bloodlines%20is%20invoked%2C%20we%20should%20ready%20ourselves%20for%20reproductive%20totalitarianisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20whenever%20demon%20demographics%20are%20evoked%2C%20it%20should%20recall%20Nazi%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Demon%20demographics%20%E2%80%93%20the%20numbers%20of%20%E2%80%98our%E2%80%99%20race%20needs%20to%20be%20higher%20in%20order%20to%20rule%20the%20nation%2Fregion%2Fworld%2C%20which%20is%20full%20of%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20subhuman%20races%20of%20different%20religious%20beliefs%2C%20language%20and%20cultural%20practices%20%E2%80%93%20drove%20the%20Nazi%20SS%20and%20its%20eugenics%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20sought%20to%20alter%20social%20mores%20and%20moral%20codes%20around%20sexuality%20and%20marriage%2C%20and%20constructed%20the%20woman%20as%20fit%20for%20only%20one%20purpose.%20It%20redefined%20the%20family%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20even%20as%20it%20sought%20to%20redefine%20children%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20appropriate%20looks%20and%20genes%2C%20of%20course%20%E2%80%93%20as%20national%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThreatened%20by%20the%20mythic%20large%20numbers%20of%20the%20racial%20Others%2C%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20set%20out%20to%20manage%20Aryan%20populations.%20As%20an%20instantiation%20of%20a%20reproductive%20totalitarianism%20scrounging%20off%20the%20hate%20for%20the%20Others%2C%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20Nazi%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20one%20shot%20at%20populating%20the%20Third%20Reich%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98own%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%20the%20thousand-year%20Reich%20of%20a%20pure-bred%20race%20never%20materialised.%C2%A0%20This%20is%20a%20history%20lesson%20that%20we%20should%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpramod-k-nayar%5C%22%3EPramod%20K.%20Nayar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0teaches%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692099014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15155116%2FLebensborn-III.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdemon-demographics-nazi-germany-and-the-making-of-racialised-anxiety%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Exhortations%20to%20certain%20communities%20to%20breed%20because%20they%20will%20otherwise%20be%20overrun%20by%20other%20communities%20is%20a%20political%20plank%20that%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20Nazi-era%20eugenics%20progamme%20%E2%80%93%20a%20history%20lesson%20we%20ought%20to%20learn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdemon-demograph