n%20currency%20is%20almost%20'embarrassing'%2C%20says%20the%20economist%20who%20named%20the%20group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224521%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20dollar%20notes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642dc80e2a659a0019a6906c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223390%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECFOTO%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20economist%20who%20coined%20the%20term%20'BRICS'%20believes%20the%20bloc's%20plans%20to%20create%20a%20common%20currency%20are%20'ridiculous'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELord%20Jim%20O'Neill%20waved%20away%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20group%20of%20countries%20ever%20challenging%20the%20dollar's%20dominance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOfficials%20of%20the%20five%20emerging%20economies%20meet%20next%20week%20to%20discuss%20whether%20to%20expand%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELord%20Jim%20O'Neill%2C%20the%20former%20Goldman%20Sachs%20economist%20who%20first%20gave%20the%20BRICS%20bloc%20its%20name%2C%20has%20slammed%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20five%20emerging%20nations%20ever%20collaborating%20to%20create%20a%20common%20currency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20%E2%80%93%20which%20comprises%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbrazil-president-de-dollarization-lula-brics-nations-currency-china-yuan-2023-4%3F_gl%3D1*1gzsnxq*_ga*MTY1MDQ2MjYyMy4xNjMyMTUxMDM0*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5MDgyMzE0Ny41NTkuMC4xNjkwODIzMTQ3LjYwLjAuMA..%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20calling%20for%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20end%20the%20dollar's%20dominance%20as%20the%20world's%20premier%20reserve%20currency%2C%20and%20Brazilian%20president%20Luiz%20In%C3%A1cio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20has%20called%20for%20a%20common%20trading%20note%20between%20them.%C