%2F15153118%2FH20230815136672.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20compile%20a%20speech%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20He%20has%20now%20delivered%20ten%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findependence-day-modi-speech-slavery-manipur%5C%22%3EIndependence%20Day%20addresses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20clear%20pattern%20emerges.%20He%20will%20claim%20sole%20credit%20for%20every%20achievement%2C%20often%20appropriating%20inevitable%20progress%20as%20a%20major%20success%3B%20he%20will%20ignore%20facts%20and%20deftly%20disregard%20past%20promises%2C%20and%20brush%20aside%20legitimate%20concerns%20of%20the%20people.%20His%20rhetoric%20often%20has%20a%20lofty%20vision%20that%20is%20devoid%20of%20a%20plan%20of%20action.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20given%20us%20a%20%E2%80%98personal%20guarantee%E2%80%99%20that%20India%20will%20become%20the%20third-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20Sounds%20impressive%20at%20first%20and%20hollow%20after%20we%20realise%20that%20in%202013%20itself%20a%20report%20estimated%20that%20India%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20by%202028.%20As%20long%20as%20policymakers%20avert%20missteps%20like%20demonetisation%2C%20a%20badly%20designed%20GST%2C%20and%20unplanned%20lockdowns%2C%20we%20(relying%20on%20a%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysis)%20can%20guarantee%20that%20we%20will%20be%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20by%202075.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20guaranteeing%20the%20inevitable%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20mentioned%20how%20before%202014%2C%20India%20was%20grouped%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98fragile%20five%E2%80%99%20economies.%20Between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20averaged%207.8%25.%20In%20the%20year%202013-14%2C%20our%20supposedly%20%E2%80%98fragile%E2%80%99%20economy%20was%20growing%20at%206.4%25%3B%20and%20has%20now%20averaged%205.7%25%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20India%20has%20drastically%20lost%20growth%20momentum%20and%20the%20people%20are%20suffering.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20functionaries%20may%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20ignoring%20facts%2C%20but%20common%20people%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20the%20youth%20hear%20the%20prime%20minister%20proclaim%20that%20%E2%80%98this%20country%20will%20provide%20you%20with%20unlimited%20opportunities%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20worry%E2%80%99%20they%20are%20not%20assured%20but%20overcome%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20disillusionment.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20unemployment%20has%20remained%20above%2022%25%20since%202014.%20The%20mismanagement%20of%20the%20economy%20has%20shrunk%20the%20job%20market%20forcing%20people%20out%20of%20the%20workforce.%20The%20government%20could%20have%20stepped%20up%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20turn%20its%20back%20and%20disregard%20the%20plight%20of%20our%20youth.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20Personnel%20informed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20between%202014%20and%202022%2C%2022%20crore%20government%20job%20applications%20were%20received%20whereas%20only%207.2%20lakhs%20were%20provided%20employment.%20For%20every%201%2C000%20applications%2C%20only%203%20jobs%20are%20being%20created%20in%20the%20government%20sector.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20worse%20is%20the%20continuous%20drop%20in%20recruitment.%20The%20number%20of%20candidates%20appointed%20has%20dropped%2070%25%20since%202014-15.%20In%202021-22%2C%20only%2038%2C850%20candidates%20were%20recruited%20against%201.86%20crore%20applications.%20The%20references%20to%20MUDRA%20Yojana%20as%20a%20serial%20job%20creator%20are%20misplaced.%20Almost%2080%25%20of%20the%20loans%20in%202021-22%20are%20in%20the%20Shishu%20category%20where%20the%20loan%20amount%20is%20less%20than%20Rs%2050%2C000.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youth%20have%20fewer%20opportunities%20because%20the%20marquee%20projects%20have%20not%20come%20through.%20In%20his%202014%20speech%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20called%20upon%20the%20world%20to%20%E2%80%98come%2C%20make%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%20The%20target%20was%20to%20create%2010%20crore%20jobs%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20by%202022.%20Between%202016%20and%202023%2C%2015%20lakh%20manufacturing%20jobs%20have%20been%20lost.%20However%2C%20we%20cannot%20let%20facts%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20speech.%20Past%20promises%20must%20be%20disregarded%20wherever%20convenient.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20do%20not%20hear%20of%20doubling%20farmer%20incomes%20anymore%2C%20or%20the%20100%20SMART%20cities%2C%20or%20houses%20for%20all%2C%20or%20electricity%20in%20every%20house.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20concern%20with%20generative%20AI%20is%20that%20without%20context%2C%20it%20produces%20results%20that%20may%20vary%20significantly%20from%20the%20issue%20at%20hand.%20ChatGPT%20often%20creates%20hyperlinks%20that%20do%20not%20exist.%20Similarly%2C%20while%20listening%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20it%20appeared%20to%20be%20laden%20with%20hyperbole%20and%20steeped%20in%20fiction.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20people%20are%20concerned%20with%20rising%20inflation%20but%20the%20prime%20minister%20brushed%20aside%20those%20issues%20with%20aplomb%2C%20claiming%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20able%20to%20control%20inflation%20successfully.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20released%20inflation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fat-15-month-high-retail-inflation-in-july-jumped-to-7-44-owing-to-soaring-vegetable-prices%5C%22%3Enumbers%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2014%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20they%20tell%20us%20that%20retail%20inflation%20is%20at%20a%2015-month%20high%20and%20vegetable%20prices%20have%20increased%2038%25%20month-on-month%20and%2037%25%20year-on-year.%20Persistently%20high%20fuel%20and%20LPG%20prices%20have%20been%20hurting%20common%20people%20for%20months%20now.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dissonance%20between%20claims%20from%20Red%20Fort%20and%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20not%20new.%20Today%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20once%20again%20spoke%20of%20implementing%20%E2%80%98One%20Rank%2C%20One%20Pension%E2%80%99%2C%20perhaps%20forgetting%20that%20a%20day%20before%20his%202015%20Independence%20Day%20address%2C%20jawans%20protesting%20peacefully%20in%20Delhi%20were%20allegedly%20manhandled%20by%20police%20forces.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20stressed%20upon%20women-led%20development%20and%20we%20must%20hope%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals.jpg%204928w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-15401%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEx-servicemen%20returning%20their%20medals%20during%20their%20agitation%20for%20the%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20(OROP)%20scheme%20in%202015.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%20Photo%20by%20Subhav%20Shukla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20anxious%20to%20leave%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%20Bombastic%20statements%20without%20positive%20change%20cannot%20achieve%20that.%20For%20three%20months%20now%2C%20people%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20brutal%20conflict.%20It%20is%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20duty%20to%20step%20in%20and%20work%20towards%20building%20peace.%20People%20will%20recall%20how%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20initiated%20dialogue%20processes%20in%20Assam%20and%20Mizoram%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20in%201985%20and%20the%20Mizoram%20Peace%20Accord%20in%201986.%20In%20both%20Assam%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20Congress%20governments%20were%20asked%20to%20either%20step%20down%20or%20fresh%20elections%20called%20to%20legitimise%20the%20peace%20process.%20We%20need%20more%20leaders%20who%20can%20sacrifice%20power.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20yearning%20for%20a%20fresh%20vision%20that%20places%20the%20vulnerable%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20policymaking.%20The%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20enacted%20progressive%20laws%20to%20aid%20gig%20workers%2C%20ensure%20robust%20healthcare%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20and%20guarantee%20a%20minimum%20income%20to%20all%20its%20citizens.%20In%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20government%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20its%20people%20and%20is%20offering%20them%20a%20caring%20government.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20pro-farmer%20and%20pro-Adivasi%20policies%20have%20led%20to%20rural%20rejuvenation.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20government%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20welfare-oriented%20plan%20of%20action%20that%20provides%20relief%20to%20the%20poorest%20and%20offers%20them%20a%20real%20opportunity%20to%20prosper.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20exhausted%20his%20ten%20speeches%20but%20still%20has%20eight%20months%20in%20government%20to%20right%20the%20wrongs.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20hoping%20we%20see%20some%20constructive%20change.%20Happy%2