and%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20such%20moment%2C%20Kiara%20candidly%20talked%20to%20Jawans%20and%20took%20their%20questions%20as%20the%20stage%20was%20set%20to%20wrap%20multiple%20days%20of%20rigorous%20shoots%20filled%20with%20activities%20and%20challenges.%20Jawans%20playfully%20delved%20into%20Kiara's%20personal%20life%20too%2C%20reminding%20us%20all%20of%20the%20shared%20human%20experiences%20that%20connect%20us.%20The%20question%20posed%20to%20Kiara%20was%20simple%20yet%20relatable-what%20was%20the%20first%20dish%20she%20cooked%20after%20her%20marriage%3F%20As%20she%20pondered%2C%20her%20smile%20widened%2C%20and%20her%20honesty%20won%20hearts.%20She%20quirkily%20shared%20that%2C%20up%20to%20that%20point%2C%20she%20might%20have%20only%20managed%20to%20boil%20water.%20Female%20Jawan%20who%20posed%20the%20question%20loved%20her%20honesty%20and%20her%20response%20was%20met%20with%20laughter%20from%20other%20jawans%20and%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20turns%20out%20that%20her%20husband%20loves%20to%20cook.%20Kiara%20shared%20that%20Sidharth%20particularly%20excels%20in%20making%20bread.%20The%20couple%20got%20married%20on%20Feb%207%20this%20year.%20Their%20wedding%20pictures%20are%20the%20most-liked%20Instagram%20post%20in%20India.%20They%20shared%20screen%20space%20in%20%3Cem%3EShershaah%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20their%20love%20story%20began.%3Cem%3E%20Shershaah%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20biographical%20film%20based%20on%20Captain%20Vikram%20Batra's%20life%20who%20got%20martyred%20in%20the%20Kargil%20war.%20While%20visiting%20the%20border%20outpost%20at%20Amritsar's%20Attari%2C%20Kiara%20remembered%20times%20when%20they%20were%20shooting%20this%20film%20in%20which%20her%20Sidharth%20played%20a%20character%20in%20uniform.%20Kiara%20revealed%20that%20she%20spent%20time%20with%20the%20families%20of%20Jawan%20to%20prepare%20for%20her%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20another%20Jawan's%20question%2C%20Kiara%20revealed%20what%20Sidharth%20calls