3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejangal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ezameen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20water%2C%20forests%20and%20land%20%E2%80%93%20without%20sparing%20a%20thought%20for%20themselves.%20We%20celebrate%20Independence%20Day%20now%2C%20but%20these%20same%20issues%20persist%20and%20have%20gotten%20worse.%20We%20still%20use%20the%20same%20oppressive%20British%20penal%20laws%20and%20more%20Adivasi%2C%20Moolnivasi%20and%20Dalit%20people%20have%20died%20or%20been%20imprisoned%20in%20land-related%20conflicts%20since%20this%20so-called%20independence.%20What%20we%20have%20today%20is%20thus%20a%20false%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20words%20of%20Mangesh%20Narote%20of%20Besewada%20village%20of%20Gadchiroli%20district%20in%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20district%2C%20a%20protest%20at%20Todgatta%2C%20against%20iron%20mining%20in%20Damkondawahi%20and%20Surjagarh%20has%20been%20afoot%20for%20the%20past%20150%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Madia-Gond%20Adivasi%20community.%20Representatives%20from%20over%2070%20villages%20have%20been%20taking%20turns%20to%20occupy%20a%20stretch%20of%20land%20in%20Todgatta.%20The%20Damkondawadi%20Bachao%20Andolan%20thus%20ensures%20that%20its%20participants%20can%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20while%20keeping%20up%20the%20protest%20against%20multiple%20new%20and%20expanding%20mining%20projects%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20in%202005%2C%2025%20mining%20projects%20were%20proposed%20in%20Gadchiroli%20district.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%20Lloyd%E2%80%99s%20Metals%20and%20Energy%20Private%20Limited%2C%20in%20Surjagarh%2C%20has%20been%20operating%20an%20iron%20mine%20on%20and%20off%20since%202007.%20It%20was%20granted%20environmental%20clearance%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20through%20what%20protesters%20say%20was%20a%20rigged%20public%20consultation%20%E2%80%93%20to%20expand%20its%20capacity%20from%203%20million%20tonnes%20per%20annum%20or%20MTPA%20to%2010%20MTPA%2C%20and%20start%20a%20crushing%20and%20processing%20plant%20in%20Aidri%2C%20Malampadi%20and%20Bande%20villages.%20This%20mine%20encroaches%20upon%20the%20land%20already%20granted%20to%20people%20from%20surrounding%20Adivasi%20villages%20as%20part%20of%20their%20community%20forest%20rights%20land%20under%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%2C%202006.%20According%20to%20protesters%20from%20Todgatta%2C%20Lloyd%E2%80%99s%20also%20conducted%20a%20public%20hearing%20two%20months%20ago%20for%20a%20steel%20processing%20plant%20in%20Konsari%20of%20Gadchiroli%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20six%20new%20mines%20spanning%204%2C684%20hectares%20have%20been%20proposed%20and%20leased%20through%20a%20composite%20mining%20lease%20to%20five%20companies%3A%20Omsairam%20Steels%20and%20Alloys%20Private%20Limited%2C%20JSW%20Steels%20Limited%2C%20Sunflag%20Iron%20and%20Steel%20Company%20Limited%2C%20Universal%20Industrial%20Equipment%20and%20Technical%20Services%20Private%20Limited%2C%20and%20Natural%20Resources%20Energy%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20four-lane%20highway%20was%20started%20but%20rapidly%20shut%20due%20to%20strong%20community%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20although%20the%20land%20for%20the%20new%20mines%20falls%20within%20traditional%20boundaries%20of%20forest%20use%20and%20occupation%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20recognised%20these%20traditional%20boundaries%20in%20the%20community%20forest%20rights%20(CFR)%20that%20have%20been%20granted%20to%20the%20nearby%2013%20and%20more%20Adivasi%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20granted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esuo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emotu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CFR%20in%202015%20to%20villages%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20mountain%2C%20but%20it%20only%20granted%20half%20of%20the%20traditionally%20occupied%20land%20and%20did%20not%20include%20any%20land%20from%20the%20mountain%20in%20the%20CFR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20left%20the%20entire%20mountain%20range%20vulnerable%20to%20mining%20and%20has%20also%20limited%20surrounding%20communities%E2%80%99%20legal%20claim%20on%20the%20mountain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EExploitation%20of%20land%20and%20livelihood%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Lloyd%E2%80%99s%20mine%20came%20up%20in%20Surjagarh%2C%20agriculture%2C%20health%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20life%20in%20the%20region%20have%20severely%20suffered%20due%20to%20red%20iron%20oxide%20discharge%2C%20chemical%20effluents%2C%20and%20large%20amount%20of%20debris.%20The%20fresh%20water%20in%20the%20region%20has%20turned%20red%20and%20is%20unusable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121034%2FIMG-20230725-WA0153.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121034%2FIMG-20230725-WA0153.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121034%2FIMG-20230725-WA0153-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121034%2FIMG-20230725-WA0153-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERed%20water%20in%20Surjagarh.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20an%20Adivasi%20man%2C%20Ajay%20Topo%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20Malampadi%20village.%20Topo%20had%20been%20worried%20because%20debris%20had%20overrun%20his%20agricultural%20field%20in%20the%20monsoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20forest-based%20livelihoods%20like%20those%20of%20tendu%20leaf%20collectors%20have%20been%20severely%20impacted%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20mining%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20said%20that%20all%20food%20and%20medicines%20for%20illnesses%20like%20stomach%20aches%2C%20fever%2C%20headaches%2C%20snake%20and%20scorpion%20bites%2C%20etc.%2C%20along%20with%20the%20timber%20and%20bamboo%20needed%20for%20building%20houses%20came%20from%20the%20forest%20earlier.%20There%20was%20also%20plenty%20of%20fresh%20water.%20%E2%80%9COur%20material%20needs%20were%20completely%20met%20by%20the%20forest%20and%20we%20rarely%20purchased%20anything.%20Our%20sacred%20deities%20were%20also%20in%20the%20mountain%20and%20we%20used%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20there.%20Now%20the%20company%2C%20and%20its%20police%2C%20do%20not%20let%20us%20enter%20our%20own%20lands%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20said.%20This%20was%20a%20common%20account%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fin-gadchiroli-the-mining-of-another-adivasi-god%5C%22%3EIn%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20Mining%20of%20Another%20Adivasi%20God%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20health%2C%20according%20to%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FOlarewaju-Oluseyi-Ifatimehin%2Fpublication%2F309927523_ENVIRONMENTAL_IMPACTS_OF_IRON_ORE_MINING_ON_QUALITY_OF_SURFACE_WATER_AND_ITS_HEALTH_IMPLICATION_ON_THE_INHABITANTS_OF_ITAKPE%2Flinks%2F5826d30308aecfd7b8c04cbb%2FENVIRONMENTAL-IMPACTS-OF-IRON-ORE-MINING-ON-QUALITY-OF-SURFACE-WATER-AND-ITS-HEALTH-IMPLICATION-ON-THE-INHABITANTS-OF-ITAKPE.pdf%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%202016%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Current%20Multidisciplinary%20Studies%2C%20mining%20of%20iron%20ore%20causes%20irreversible%20damage%20to%20underground%20water%20systems%20and%20surface%20water%2C%20thereby%20severely%20affecting%20the%20health%20of%20those%20using%20the%20water.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20average%20lethal%20dose%20of%20iron%20is%20200-250%20mg%20per%20kg%20of%20body%20weight%2C%20but%20death%20has%20occurred%20following%20the%20ingestion%20of%20doses%20as%20low%20as%2040%20mg%20per%20kg%20of%20body%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20been%20known%20to%20suffer%20from%20various%20diseases%20such%20as%20catharsis%2C%20dehydration%20and%20gastro-intestinal%20irritation.%20Iron%20ore%20can%20interfere%20with%20normal%20body%20fluid%20regulation%20even%20long%20after%20a%20mine%20has%20been%20closed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121224%2FIMG-20230725-WA0169.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121224%2FIMG-20230725-WA0169.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121224%2FIMG-20230725-WA0169-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121224%2FIMG-20230725-WA0169-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668169%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFresh%20water%20in%20Surjagarh.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECriminalisation%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20everything%20takes%20place%20in%20a%20collective%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20advocate%20Lalsu%20Nogoti%2C%20referring%20not%20only%20to%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiejournal.in%2Farticle%2Ftodgatta-protestors-find-support-in-community%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20protest%20set-up%20at%20Todgatta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20also%20to%20everyday%20life%2C%20for%20both%20of%20which%20villagers%20convene%20at%20the%20Gotul%20or%20village%20square.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gotul%20is%20a%20constant%20yet%20fluid%20space%20that%20simultaneously%20functions%20as%20a%20university%2C%20a%20court%2C%20an%20entertainment%20centre%2C%20an%20information%20hub%2C%20and%20a%20community%20centre.%20One%20does%20not%20sit%20still%20in%20a%20Gotul%20%E2%80%93%20adults%20and%20elders%20engage%20in%20basket-weaving%2C%20rope-making%2C%20and%20even%20plowing%20while%20the%20children%20and%20youth%20learn%20from%20watching.%20There%20is%20no%20admission%20required%2C%20and%20no%20graduation%20date%2C%20for%20this%20practical%20and%20generationally-transferred%20education.%20The%20Gotul%20also%20acts%20as%20a%20court%2C%20addressing%20community%20issues%20in%20a%20democratic%20way.%20Importantly%2C%20the%20Gotul%20acts%20as%20the%20space%20wherein%20people%20share%20stories%20and%20wisdom%2C%20news%20about%20national%20and%20international%20issues%2C%20and%20currently%2C%20carry%20out%20their%20democratic%20protest%2C%20along%20with%20discussions%20and%20decisions%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20Lule%20Mattami%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20Yuva%20Chhatra%20Sangathan%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20traditional%20gram%20sabha%20we%20have%20a%20space%20to%20speak%20freely.%20We%20all%20discuss%20the%20next%20steps%20of%20the%20protest%20together%2C%20and%20help%20each%20other%20learn%20and%20understand%20what%20to%20do.%20If%20someone%20is%20unhappy%20with%20a%20decision%2C%20we%20try%20to%20listen%2C%20understand%20and%20come%20to%20a%20common%20consensus%20using%20our%20traditional%20processes%20of%20decision-making.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20village%20representatives%20%E2%80%93%20each%20one%20representing%2010%20people%20back%20home%20and%20who%20attend%20in%20rotational%20shifts%20of%20a%20few%20days%20each%20%E2%80%93%20at%20assemble%20at%20the%20Todgatta%20Gotul%20and%20start%20their%20meeting%20by%20paying%20their%20respects%20to%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20Rani%20Durgavati%2C%20Savitribai%20Phule%2C%20Jotiba%20Phule%2C%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Bhagat%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15120834%2FIMG_20230813_090712-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15120834%2FIMG_20230813_090712-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15120834%2FIMG_20230813_090712-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15120834%2FIMG_20230813_090712-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668166%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20protest%20at%20Todgatta%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Gadchiroli.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20read%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20constitution%20translated%20into%20Madia%2C%20and%20then%20take%20attendance%20while%20collectively%20discussing%20challenges%20and%20important%20developments%20in%20the%20protest.%20Mangesh%20Narote%2C%20quoted%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20this%20piece%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20very%20existence%20of%20this%20protest%20village%20%5BTodgatta%5D%20reiterates%20the%20reason%20for%20our%20protest.%20This%20sort%20of%20sustenance%20would%20simply%20not%20be%20possible%20in%20the%20city.%20It%20would%20be%20hot%2C%20our%20tarp%20would%20fly%20away%2C%20and%20we%20would%20have%20no%20way%20to%20feed%20or%20sustain%20ourselves.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20meet%20our%20collective%20protest%20needs%20only%20because%20we%20are%20in%20the%20forest.%20How%20can%20anyone%20survive%20without%20jal-jangal-zameen%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20this%20democratic%20and%20peaceful%20protest%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20criminalised%20by%20the%20state-corporate%20nexus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20ask%20how%20the%20model%20of%20%E2%80%98s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikaas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20motto%2C%20translating%20to%20%E2%80%98with%20all%2C%20development%20for%20all%E2%80%99)%E2%80%99%20serves%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERakesh%20Alam%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20Yuva%20Chhatra%20Sangathan%2C%20and%20Pattu%20Pottami%2C%20Gram%20Sabha%20Adhyaksh%20of%20Dodur%20are%20united%20in%20their%20takedown%20of%20the%20way%20locals%E2%80%99%20rights%20have%20been%20trampled%20upon%20to%20make%20way%20for%20corporates.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20thing%20they%20did%20to%20start%20the%20mining%20process%20in%20Damkondwahi%20was%20to%20build%20a%20road%20and%20establish%20Jio%20signal%20towers.%20Then%20they%20built%20police%20stations.%20We%20are%20not%20against%20roads%20or%20connectivity%2C%20but%20we%20know%20that%20these%20are%20for%20the%20company%20officials%2C%20not%20for%20us.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20know%20that%20the%20police%20stations%20are%20not%20for%20our%20safety%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20they%20have%20been%20built%20to%20repress%20our%20mass%20dissent%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20and%20Pottami%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGanesh%20Korsa%2C%20member%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20Yuva%20Chhatra%20Sangathan%2C%20also%20expresses%20his%20concern%20at%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20police%20camps%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20completely%20take%20over%20our%20mountain%20and%20put%20up%20police%20camps%2C%20we%20will%20not%20even%20be%20able%20to%20move%20freely%20between%20out%20own%20houses%20and%20villages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgadchiroli-adivasis-mining-displacement%5C%22%3EGadchiroli%20Ground%20Zero%3A%20The%20Adivasi%20Struggle%20Against%20%E2%80%98Development%E2%80%99%20That%20Displaces%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtesters%20in%20Todgatta%20say%20the%20mine%20has%20also%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20violence%20against%20women.%20They%20stress%20that%20allegation%20of%20violence%20does%20not%20just%20mean%20physical%20violence%20from%20the%20police%2C%20but%20also%20encompasses%20the%20mental%20hardships%20of%20becoming%20a%20widow%2C%20dealing%20with%20alcohol%20addiction%20and%20violence%20within%20the%20home%2C%20ensuring%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20their%20children%2C%20and%20many%20other%20such%20experiences%20that%20cannot%20be%20articulated.%20A%20Nari%20Mukti%20Samiti%20is%20currently%20being%20formed%2C%20the%20process%20of%20which%20is%20being%20led%20by%20Sushila%20Narote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20villagers%20point%20out%20how%20the%20takeover%20was%20rushed%20and%20kept%20them%20out.%20On%20October%2027%2C%202022%2C%20the%20public%20consultation%20for%20the%20Lloyd%E2%80%99s%20mine%E2%80%99s%20expansion%20and%20crushing%20plant%20took%20place%20at%20Gadchiroli%20city.%20Just%20before%20the%20consultation%2C%20buses%20full%20of%20people%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20bribed%20by%20the%20company%2C%20arrived.%20Such%20people%2C%20who%20villagers%20say%20had%20turned%20up%20intoxicated%2C%20took%20over%20the%20venue.%20The%20police%20prevented%20movement%20leaders%20from%20entering%20the%20consultation%20area.%20Thus%20none%20of%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20in%20Surjagarh%20Patti%20%E2%80%93%20the%20area%20which%20would%20actually%20face%20the%20impact%20%E2%80%93%20were%20consulted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20are%20quickly%20labelled%20%E2%80%9CMaoists%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Canti-national.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121504%2FIMG-20230725-WA0015.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121504%2FIMG-20230725-WA0015.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121504%2FIMG-20230725-WA0015-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121504%2FIMG-20230725-WA0015-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668171%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESurjagarh.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20activists%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Nitin%20Padda%2C%20Ramdas%20Gera%2C%20Sainu%20Gotu%2C%20Shiela%20Gota%2C%20Pattu%20Pottami%2C%20Jai%20Sri%20Virda%2C%20Sushila%20Narote%2C%20Rakesh%20Alam%2C%20and%20Mangesh%20Narote%20amongst%20many%20others%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20Section%20110%20(punishment%20of%20abetment%20if%20person%20abetted%20does%20act%20with%20different%20intention%20from%20that%20of%20abettor.)%20and%20353%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20public%20servant%20from%20discharge%20of%20his%20duty)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protesters%20say%20they%20have%20faced%20police%20beatings%20and%20have%20been%20implicated%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Frights%2Fmahesh-raut-forest-rights-bhima-koregon%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Efalse%20cases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Some%20say%20they%20were%20brutally%20lathi%20charged%20and%20locked%20away%20without%20any%20clear%20accusations%20levelled.%20While%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Fthree-killed-in-surjagarh-mine-accident-2-serious%2Farticleshow%2F102485061.cms%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20death%20of%20three%20mine%20workers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%206%20was%20fortunately%20captured%20by%20the%20media%2C%20the%20deaths%20of%20other%20mine%20workers%20from%20nearby%20and%20migrant%20communities%20never%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FPSI-2021%2FPSI_2021_as_on_31-12-2021.pdf%5C%22%3E2021%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NCRB)%20data%20on%20prisons%2C%20seven%20in%2010%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E5%2C54%2C034%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20people%20in%20prison%20in%20Indian%20jails%20are%20under%20trial%20and%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Emajority%20are%20from%20marginalised%20castes%20(21.21%25%20SCs%2C%2010.78%25%20STs%2C%2035.83%25%20OBC).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20protest%20democratically%2C%20the%20government%20should%20listen%20to%20us%20and%20treat%20us%20equally.%20But%20they%20are%20obsessed%20with%20making%20the%20big%20money%20bigger%2C%20and%20squashing%20the%20small%20even%20further.%20They%20fail%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20person%20does%20not%20become%20big%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20made%20up%20of%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narote%20stresses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20tree%2C%20the%20roots%20are%20sturdy%20and%20big%20and%20play%20the%20role%20of%20taking%20in%20water.%20The%20branches%20and%20leaves%2C%20although%20very%20small%2C%20are%20crucial%20in%20that%20they%20absorb%20sunlight%20and%20provide%20nutrition%20to%20the%20tree.%20Without%20the%20leaves%2C%20the%20roots%20cannot%20exist%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20this%2C%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnjali%20is%20a%20cultural%20activist%20learning%20with%20indigenous%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20part%20of%20Yugma%20Collective.%20Shubha%20is%20a%20member%20of%20Yugma%20Collective%20and%20is%20currently%20studying%20legal%20aspects%20of%20forest-based%20movements.%20Gowri%20is%20a%20graduate%20in%20Sociology%20and%20is%20engaged%20with%20and%20learning%20from%20labour%20rights%20movements.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692091852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15120333%2FIMG-20230725-WA0242.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findependence-mining-gadchiroli-adivasi-protest-maharashtra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iron%20mining%20in%20Damkondawahi%20and%20Surjagarh%20have%20affected%20life%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20turning%20fresh%20water%20red%20and%20covering%20agricultural%20fields%20in%20debris.%20Adivasis%20have%20been%20sustaining%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20for%20months%20how.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findependence-mining-gadchiroli-adivasi-protest-maharashtra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Remembering%20the%20Rebel%2C%20Underground%20Movie%20Theater%20That%20Gave%20Hope%20to%20