0broke%20out%2C%20the%20regional%20branch%20of%20the%20Investigative%20Committee%2C%20which%20probes%20major%20incidents%2C%20announced%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20fire%20occurred%20during%20car%20maintenance%20work%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20bang%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20people%20were%20injured%20and%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20committee%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20nearby%20buildings%20and%20cars%20were%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20criminal%20case%20has%20been%20opened%20to%20establish%20the%20circumstances%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20fire%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Couldn't%20see%20anything'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState-run%20news%20agencies%20TASS%20and%20Ria%20Novosti%20reported%20that%20the%20fire%20had%20been%20extinguished%2C%20citing%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMakhachkala%2C%20a%20city%20of%20over%20600%2C000%20on%20the%20Caspian%20Sea%2C%20is%20the%20capital%20of%20Dagestan%2C%20a%20Russian%20republic%20bordering%20Chechnya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20was%20heard%20shortly%20before%2010%3A00%20pm%20(1900%20GMT)%20on%20Monday%2C%20Sergei%20Melikov%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Dagestan%20administration%2C%20announced%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20witness%20quoted%20by%20Russian%20daily%20newspaper%20Izvestia%20said%20the%20fire%20started%20in%20an%20area%20where%20cars%20were%20parked%20and%20spread%20to%20the%20petrol%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20explosion%2C%20everything%20fell%20on%20our%20heads.%20We%20couldn't%20see%20anything%20any%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20witness%2C%20who%20was%20not%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideo%20footage%20released%20by%20Russia's%20emergency%20situations%20ministry%20showed%20firefighters%20trying%20to%20extinguish%20huge%20flames%20near%20burnt-out%20vehicles%2C%20as%20rescue%20workers%20examined%20the%20rubble%20of%20a%20building%20with%20flashlights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20had%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20around%20600%20square%20metres%20(6%2C450%20square%20feet)%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20260%20firefighters%20had%20been%20deployed%20ot%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20Il-76%20aircraft%20carrying%20medical%20equipment%20had%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Makhachkala%20to%20evacuate%20the%20seriously%20injured%20to%20Moscow%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelikov%20said%20that%20the%20evacuation%20operation%20had%20since%20been%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dagestan%20government%20declared%20August%2015%20a%20day%20of%20mourning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BState%20flags%20will%20be%20flown%20at%20half%20mast%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20and%20cultural%20institutions%20and%20TV%20channels%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20cancel%20entertainment%20events%20and%20programmes%2C%26quot%3B%20Melikov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692090600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fhumeomo8_russian-blast-_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feverything-fell-on-our-heads-35-killed-in-blast-at-russian-fuel-station-4299756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2035%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20explosion%20that%20created%20a%20huge%20fire%20ball%20at%20a%20fuel%20station%20in%20Russia's%20remote%20Caucasus%20republic%20of%20Dagestan%2C%20spurring%20condolences%20from%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feverything-fell-on-our-heads-35-killed-in-blast-at-russian-fuel-station-4299756%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2