0-crowd-in-australia-semi-final-millie-bright-says-12940397%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Big%20OBC%20Outreach%2C%20PM%20Announces%20Scheme%20To%20Help%20Traditional%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20outreach%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20next%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20announced%20a%20scheme%20to%20help%20those%20earning%20a%20living%20through%20traditional%20skills.%20The%20scheme%20will%20have%20an%20allocation%20of%20Rs%2013%2C000-Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20of%20blunting%20the%20opposition's%20efforts%20to%20attract%20the%20OBC%20vote%20through%20moves%20like%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20which%20is%20being%20planned%20in%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20announced%20the%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20and%20said%20the%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20helping%20those%20with%20traditional%20skills%2C%20who%20use%20their%20hands%20and%20basic%20tools%20to%20make%20a%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20largely%20from%20the%20OBC%20sections.%20They%20can%20be%20people%20like%20carpenters%2C%20goldsmiths%2C%20masons%2C%20washermen%20and%20women%2C%20and%20barbers.%20To%20give%20such%20workers%20strength%2C%20we%20will%20launch%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Vishwakarma%20Jayanti%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwakarma%20Jayanti%2C%20which%20will%20be%20celebrated%20on%20September%2017%20this%20year%2C%20sees%20prayer%20events%20being%20organised%20across%20the%20country%20to%20worship%20the%20deity%20of%20craftsmen%20and%20architects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20resolution%20at%20the%20second%20mega%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20a%20fair%20hearing%20for%20all%20socially%2C%20educationally%20and%20economically%20backward%20communities%3B%20and%2C%20as%20a%20first%20step%2C%20implement%20the%20caste%20census.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20decision%20to%20conduct%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20and%20the%20socio-economic%20survey%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20caste%20census%20but%20said%20it%20will%20hear%20the%20petitions%20against%20it%20on%20August%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20contended%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20cannot%20conduct%20the%20census%20as%20it%20violates%20a%20constitutional%20mandate%2C%20which%20states%20that%20such%20exercises%20can%20only%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20Centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20after%20its%20formation%2C%20the%20Justice%20G%20Rohini-headed%20Commission%20for%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBC%20groups%20has%20also%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20July%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OBC%20vote%20will%20also%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20this%20year%2C%20especially%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20a%20high%20population%20of%20people%20from%20these%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692088620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F17alfef_pm-modi-red-fort-650_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20outreach%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20next%20year%2