me%20if%20they%20want%20to%20go%20out%20with%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20revealed%20that%20one%20thing%20that%20affects%20his%20social%20life%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20doesn't%20drink.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20used%20to%20drink%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20but%20later%20he%20cut%20out%20drinking%20to%20avoid%20the%20extra%20calories.%20He%20also%20drank%20it%20in%20the%20morning%20with%20breakfast%20and%20isn't%20much%20of%20a%20conversationalist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F08%2F11%2Fim-45-a-billionaire-obsessed-with-staying-young-and-hard-to-date%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20and%20I%20have%20a%20protocol%20in%20the%20house%20where%20there's%20no%20exchange%20of%20like%2C%20'Good%20morning.%20How%20are%20you%3F'%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20go%20to%20bed%20early%2C%20I%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20and%20I%20have%20these%20four%20or%20five%20hours%20of%20concentrated%20thought%20where%20I%20can%20think%20about%20these%20really%20big%20pictures%20and%20try%20to%20pull%20myself%20out%20of%20my%20situation%20and%20just%20be%20as%20sober%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20probe%20myself%20to%20deep%20levels%2C%20but%20you%20can%20get%20knocked%20off%20so%20fast.%20Someone%20saying%2C%20'How%20are%20you%3F%20How%20was%20your%20sleep%3F'%20can%20knock%20me%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20made%20his%20fortune%20in%20his%2030s%20when%20he%20sold%20his%20payment%20processing%20company%20Braintree%20Payment%20Solutions%20to%20eBay%20for%20%24800%20million%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Epublished%20an%20article%20on%20Mr%20Johnson%20and%20his%20efforts%20to%20regain%20his%20youth%20through%20a%20rigorous%20plan%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20of%20doctors%20call%20%26