othing.%20It%20thrives%20on%20propaganda%20with%20its%20control%20on%20the%20media%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20who%20is%20otherwise%20known%20for%20speaking%20in%20measured%20words%2C%20of%20late%2C%20resembles%20his%20friend%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20attacking%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Reacting%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Nitish%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESawal%20kya%20thaa%2C%20kya%20kya%20bol%20gaye%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(He%20spoke%20gibberish%2C%20ignoring%20the%20question)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5BModi%20and%20BJP%5D%20are%20frightened%20of%20our%20unity.%20It%20began%20with%20the%20oppositions%E2%80%99%20conclave%20in%20Patna.%20We%20grew%20in%20number%20and%20our%20resolve%20at%20our%20Bengaluru%20meet%20also%20grew.%20At%20the%20next%20meeting%20we%20will%20decide%20how%20to%20take%20the%20country%20forward%E2%80%A6the%20BJP%20will%20be%20washed%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20Nitish%20attacked%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20his%20video%20address%20to%20the%20Panchayat%20Raj%20Parishad%20in%20West%20Bengal%20named%20health%20centres%20his%20government%20had%20set%20up.%20Among%20those%2C%20he%20named%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20at%20Darbhanga%20%E2%80%93%20a%20district%20town%20in%20north%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Mithila%20region.%20The%20hospital%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20constructed%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpatna-news%2Fbihar-cm-nitish-kumar-asserts-shobhan-is-ideal-site-for-aiims-accuses-centre-of-delaying-project-for-political-reasons-101692026980286.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20led%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20back%20and%20forth%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20RJD%2C%20JD(U)%20and%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-bihar-central-agencies-ajit-pawar-tejashwi-nitish%5C%22%3EDespite%20Efforts%2C%20BJP%20Fails%20to%20Pull%20an%20%E2%80%98Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99%20in%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20leaders%20have%20come%20out%20with%20all%20guns%20blazing.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESafed%20jhooth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(white%20lies)%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20state%20health%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20pulling%20out%20the%20official%20records%20that%20testified%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20had%20given%20151%20acres%20of%20land%20on%20the%20Shobhan%20bypass%20in%20Darbhanga%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20the%20AIIMS%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20the%20state%20cabinet%20sanctioned%20Rs%20309.29%20crore%20for%20filling%20the%20land%E2%80%9D%2C%20Tejashwi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJD(U)%20president%20and%20MP%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20attacked%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20over%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20on%20August%2011%2C%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%9Cspoke%20lies%20habitually%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20came%20out%20in%20defence%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20land%20allotted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20in%20Darbhanga%20was%20not%20appropriate.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20too%20defended%20the%20prime%20minister%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CJD(U)%20and%20the%20RJD%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20take%20credit%2C%20relegated%20the%20project%20to%20backburner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20false%20claim.%20And%20despite%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20Sushil%20Modi%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20defending%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Modi%20stands%20exposed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%20ignoring%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20writer%20recently%20travelled%20to%20the%20north%20Bihar-Uttar%20Pradesh%20borders%20to%20find%20aggressive%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20cadres%20on%20the%20Bihar%20side%2C%20taking%20up%20efforts%20to%20tell%20people%20about%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20health%2C%20education%20and%20civic%20infrastructure%20with%20emphasis%20on%20empowering%20women%2C%20extremely%20backward%20classes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mandatory%20tool%20in%20present%20day%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20is%20something%20that%20JD(U)%20and%20RJD%20have%20been%20making%20their%20presence%20felt%20on.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20beefed%20up%20his%20and%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20presence%20by%20employing%20professionals.%20Besides%20the%20official%20Twitter%20handles%2C%20parody%20accounts%20counter%20the%20BJP%20IT%20cell%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98propaganda%E2%80%99.%20The%20JD(U)%2C%20initially%20lagging%20behind%20on%20the%20social%20media%20front%20has%20augmented%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20not%20made%20significant%20gains%20in%20Bihar%20after%20the%20setback%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20in%20Haryana%2C%20UP%20and%20other%20states%2C%20Modi%2C%20after%20becoming%20prime%20minister%20in%202014%20tried%20to%20build%20his%20own%20team%20of%20party%20cadres%20with%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econfidante%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Amit%20Shah.%20The%20duo%20might%20have%20succeeded%20in%20other%20states%20but%20they%20have%20failed%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrior%20to%20the%20dawn%20of%20Modi-Shah%20era%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20party%2C%20Sushil%20was%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20face%20in%20Bihar.%20A%20product%20of%20the%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20led%20%E2%80%98total%20revolution%E2%80%99%20and%20groomed%20by%20Kailashpati%20Mishra%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%2C%20Sushil%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20Bihar%20and%20a%20link%20between%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20Rooted%20in%20the%20philosophy%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20Sushil%20enjoyed%20all%20acceptance%20and%20respect%20among%20the%20cadres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Terkeshwar%20Prasad%2C%20a%20product%20of%20the%20ABVP%20and%20Renu%20Devi%2C%20of%20Durga%20Vahini%2C%20who%20replaced%20Sushil%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20after%20the%202020%20polls%20had%20grown%20under%20Sushil%E2%80%99s%20patronage.%20Even%20the%20Union%20minister%2C%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20of%20late%20known%20for%20his%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20too%20grew%20under%20Sushil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20tried%20to%20promote%20Giriraj%2C%20Nityanand%20Singh%2C%20Samrat%20Choudhary%20and%20others%20at%20Sushil%E2%80%99s%20expense.%20In%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20political%20circles%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20widely%20believed%20that%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20got%20Sushil%20out%20of%20Bihar%20by%20making%20him%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20to%20promote%20their%20own%20brand%20of%20party%20leaders%20who%20could%20work%20more%20aggressively%20against%20minorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20their%20experiment%20seems%20to%20have%20failed%20in%20the%20state.%20Giriraj%2C%20Nityanand%20and%20Samrat%20Choudhary%20have%20not%20displayed%20the%20flair%20of%20local%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20crosses%20the%20Mehrauna%20Bridge%20on%20the%20Gandak%20river%20and%20enters%20eastern%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Deoria%20district%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20influence%20grows.%20Right%20beyond%20the%20bridge%2C%20there%20is%20a%20signpost%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Vahini.%20The%20houses%20and%20shops%20along%20the%20Mehrauna-Laar-Deoria%20road%20have%20saffron%20flags%20fluttering%20on%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20streets%20are%20full%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ekanwariyas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20groups%2C%20travelling%20on%20motorcycles%2C%20jeeps%20and%20tractors%20chanting%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBol%20Bam%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shriram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99.%20There%20are%20policemen%20to%20serve%20and%20escort%20them%20respectfully.%20This%20writer%20saw%20a%20group%20of%20kanwariyas%20getting%20frenzied%20when%20they%20reached%20a%20mosque%20at%20Salempur.%20The%20policemen%20did%20little%20to%20quell%20them.%20No%20Muslims%20were%20visible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20on%20folklore.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692084607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16183438%2FScreenshot-2022-08-16-at-6.34.34-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthe