re-balakrishnan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBalakrishnan%20is%20a%20full%20professor%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20joined%20the%20private%20university%20in%202015%20after%20working%20at%20Oxford%20University%2C%20the%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20in%20Kozhikode%20and%20the%20World%20Bank.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20several%20well-regarded%20books%2C%20including%20most%20recently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fculture%2Fbooks%2Fan-uneven-economic-journey-indias-economy-from-nehru-to-modi-a-brief-history-author-pulapre-balakrishnan%2Fcid%2F1902831%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Economy%20from%20Nehru%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Permanent%20Black%20in%20association%20with%20Ashoka%20University%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20announced%20by%20Ashoka%20and%20his%20resignation%20letter%20is%20not%20public%2C%20sources%20at%20the%20university%20said%20the%20senior%20economist%20had%20decided%20to%20leave%20%E2%80%9Cin%20solidarity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20soon%20after%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20broke%20the%20story%20about%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20quitting%2C%20Ashoka%20vice-chancellor%20Somak%20Raychaudhury%20said%20the%20university%20had%20accepted%20Das%E2%80%99s%20resignation.%20Seeking%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20unhappiness%20with%20his%20research%20paper%20on%20the%202019%20elections%20that%20had%20angered%20the%20Bharatiya%20janata%20Party%2C%20Raychaudhury%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMembers%20of%20the%20faculty%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20teach%20and%20carry%20out%20research%20in%20the%20areas%20they%20choose.%20The%20university%20affords%20its%20faculty%20and%20students%20the%20most%20enabling%20environment%20for%20academic%20freedom%20at%20an%20institution%20of%20higher%20education.%20This%20academic%20freedom%20also%20applied%20to%20Mr.%20Das.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20likely%20to%20fuel%20fears%20that%20Das%E2%80%99s%20exit%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20controversy%20caused%20by%20his%20July%2025%2C%202023%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4512936%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20publicly%20dissociated%20itself%20from%20his%20research%20in%20a%20tweet%20on%20August%201%20and%20also%20questioned%20its%20quality%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20was%20not%20peer-reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20common%20practice%20for%20academics%20in%20leading%20universities%20across%20the%20world%20to%20upload%20drafts%20of%20their%20research%20for%20comment%20and%20discussion%20prior%20to%20eventual%20publication%20in%20a%20peer-reviewed%20journal%2C%20and%20Ashoka%20was%20widely%20criticised%20by%20academics%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20for%20distancing%20itself%20from%20Das%20in%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20he%20was%20hired%20in%202015%2C%20Ashoka%20University%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fashoka-university-attracts-faculty-from-across%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20noting%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfaculty%20strength%20at%20Ashoka%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20this%20year%20as%20the%20best%20academics%20and%20scholars%20join%20the%20University%20from%20India%20and%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPulapre%20Balakrishnan%2C%20Professor%20of%20Economics%2C%20shares%20his%20motivation%20to%20join%20Ashoka%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98Ashoka%20has%20projected%20itself%20as%20committed%20to%20providing%20a%20world-class%20education%20in%20the%20liberal%20arts%20in%20India.%20This%20attracted%20me%2C%20as%20education%20outside%20the%20natural%20sciences%20and%20engineering%20has%20not%20received%20its%20due%20here.%20But%20above%20all%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20aim%20to%20be%20world%20class%20in%20whatever%20you%20do.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20fallout%20on%20Ashoka%2C%20news%20of%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20further%20evidence%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaacademicfreedom.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimperilled%20state%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Ashoka%20University%20administration%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20seek%20a%20comment%20on%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20and%20will%20update%20this%20story%20when%20we%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692082486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121416%2Fcollagesab-pula.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fsecond-professor-quits-as-democratic-backsliding-row-continues-to-roil-ashoka-university%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20resignation%20of%20senior%20faculty%20member%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%20is%20likely%20to%20fuel%20fears%20that%20Sabyasachi%20Das's%20exit%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20university's%20handling%20of%20the%20controversy%20his%20paper%20on%20the%202019%20elections%20had%20caused.%20BJP%20leaders%20came%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20young%20economist.%22%2C%22author%22%