ng%20loyalists%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20Europeans%2C%20Anglo-Indians%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Jews%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Chowpatty%20Beach.%20When%20the%20meeting%20at%20Elphinstone%20Mill%20ended%2C%20the%20workers%20made%20their%20way%20to%20Charni%20Road%20and%20Marine%20Lines%20stations%20where%20they%20met%20crowds%20of%20loyalists%20returning%20from%20welcoming%20the%20Prince%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20in%20trams.%20The%20workers%20rushed%20the%20trams%2C%20beating%20up%20their%20occupants.%20Many%20trams%20were%20set%20on%20fire.%20Anyone%20wearing%20hats%20that%20were%20seen%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98loyalist%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20solar%20topees%2C%20felt%20hats%2C%20or%20the%20Parsi%20phenta%20%E2%80%93%20was%20singled%20out%20for%20attack.%20Their%20headgear%20was%20snatched%2C%20piled%20up%20in%20the%20street%20and%20burnt.%20Europeans%20and%20Anglo-Indians%20were%20singled%20out%20because%20they%20were%20associated%20with%20the%20mill%20supervisors%20who%20often%20treated%20the%20workers%20in%20a%20racist%20and%20violent%20manner.%20They%20were%20now%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20kicks%20and%20blows.%20The%20Parsis%20were%20attacked%20because%20they%20were%20known%20for%20their%20loyalism%20to%20the%20British%2C39%20as%20they%20owned%20and%20operated%20several%20mills%2C%20and%20as%20many%20of%20the%20liquor%20shops%20in%20the%20city%20were%20run%20by%20members%20of%20this%20community%20and%20they%20had%20refused%20to%20close%20them%20despite%20nationalist%20picketing.%20The%20relatively%20small%20Jewish%20community%20of%20the%20city%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20capitalist%20elite.%20When%20news%20of%20what%20was%20going%20on%20spread%2C%20workers%20came%20out%20from%20other%20mills%20and%20joined%20the%20fray.%20Some%20were%20heard%20to%20cry%20%E2%80%98Mahatma%20Gandhi%20ki%20jai%E2%80%99%20as%20they%20assaulted%20the%20loyalists.%20Even%20Parsi%20women%20were%20not%20spared%20%E2%80%93%20several%20were%20assaulted%20and%20had%20their%20saris%20torn%20from%20them.%20Two%20Anglo-Indians%2C%20two%20Parsis%2C%20and%20one%20American%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20turmoil.%20During%20the%20disturbance%2C%20four%20liquor%20shops%20were%20burnt%20down%20and%20a%20further%20135%20looted%20or%20damaged%20by%20the%20crowds.%20Intense%20fighting%20continued%20into%20the%20early%20hours%20of%2018%20November%2C%20with%20six%20policemen%20being%20killed.%20Congress%20volunteers%20who%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20were%20themselves%20beaten%3B%20some%20so%20badly%20that%20they%20died.%20Although%20martial%20law%20was%20declared%2C%20workers%20continued%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%20to%20roam%20the%20streets%20attacking%20those%20whose%20headwear%20and%20clothing%20marked%20them%20as%20loyalists.%20Some%20Parsis%20and%20Anglo-Indians%20retaliated%20by%20forming%20their%20own%20bands%2C%20which%20toured%20the%20streets%20snatching%20Gandhi%20caps%20and%20attacking%20people%20considered%20to%20be%20pro-Congress%2C%20while%20the%20police%20looked%20on%20and%20even%20helped%20them.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20nationalist%20leaders%20and%20volunteers%20joined%20with%20groups%20of%20public%20figures%20who%20went%20around%20the%20city%20exhorting%20people%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20and%20by%20this%20means%20order%20was%20eventually%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%5C%22%3EThe%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20left%20distraught%20by%20all%20this%2C%20especially%20as%20he%20had%20put%20so%20much%20stress%20on%20the%20need%20for%20complete%20nonviolence%20in%20his%20speech%20that%20day%20to%20the%20workers.%20He%20had%20rushed%20immediately%20to%20the%20scene%20on%20hearing%20of%20the%20rioting%2C%20where%20he%20was%20told%20%E2%80%98the%20most%20painful%20and%20humiliating%20story%20of%20molestation%20of%20Parsi%20sisters%E2%80%99.%20One%20elderly%20Parsi%20pleaded%20with%20him%20to%20save%20them.%20He%20was%20surrounded%20by%20crowds%20chanting%20%E2%80%98Mahatma%20Gandhi%20ki%20jai!%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20sound%20that%20%E2%80%93%20he%20said%20%E2%80%93%20merely%20grated%20on%20his%20ears.%20He%20appealed%20for%20them%20to%20go%20home.%20When%20a%20report%20came%20to%20him%20of%20violence%20in%20another%20part%20of%20the%20city%2C%20he%20went%20there%20and%20called%20for%20calm%2C%20persuading%20the%20crowd%20to%20disperse.%20He%20estimated%20that%20about%2020%2C000%20people%20were%20involved%2C%20and%20not%20all%20were%20mill%20hands.%20He%20felt%20that%20they%20knew%20what%20they%20were%20doing%2C%20being%20%E2%80%98bent%20upon%20mischief%20and%20destruction%E2%80%99.%20He%20wrote%20late%20that%20night%3A%20%E2%80%98We%20have%20a%20foretaste%20of%20swaraj.%20I%20have%20been%20put%20to%20shame.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20day%2C%2018%20November%2C%20he%20reported%20that%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20volunteers%20who%20had%20tried%20to%20intervene%20with%20workers%20in%20Parel%20had%20been%20turned%20on.%20He%20had%20personally%20seen%20them%20on%20their%20return%20with%20their%20heads%20broken%20and%20bleeding.%20Some%20had%20%E2%80%98lacerating%20wounds%E2%80%99.%20He%20accused%20the%20mill%20workers%20of%20leaving%20their%20factories%20in%20%E2%80%98criminal%20disobedience%20of%20the%20wishes%20of%20their%20masters%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%98We%20claim%20to%20have%20established%20a%20peaceful%20atmosphere%2C%20i.e.%2C%20to%20have%20attained%20by%20our%20non-violence%20sufficient%20control%20over%20the%20people%20to%20keep%20their%20violence%20under%20check.%20We%20have%20failed%20when%20we%20ought%20to%20have%20succeeded.%E2%80%99%20He%20felt%20personally%20culpable%2C%20as%20he%20had%20encouraged%20a%20spirit%20of%20defiance%20that%20he%20had%20been%20unable%20to%C2%A0control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20next%20morning%2C%20Gandhi%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20to%20go%20on%20a%20fast%20until%20peace%20had%20been%20restored%20between%20the%20different%20communities.%20He%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%98The%20swaraj%20that%20I%20have%20witnessed%20during%20the%20last%20two%20days%20has%20stunk%20in%20my%20nostrils%E2%80%99.%20The%20fast%20continued%20during%20the%2020th%20and%2021st%20as%20he%20issued%20appeals%20for%20peace.%20The%20riots%20had%20subsided%20by%2022%20November%2C%20and%20he%20broke%20his%20fast%20that%20morning.%20A%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20was%20held%20in%20the%20city%20on%2022%20and%2023%20November%20at%20which%20the%20violence%20was%20deplored.%20The%20committee%20felt%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20that%20it%20had%20exposed%20a%20%E2%80%98weak%20spot%E2%80%99%20that%20revealed%20a%20need%20for%20efforts%20to%20obtain%20better%20control%20over%20%E2%80%98all%20turbulent%20elements%20in%20society%E2%80%99.%20Congress%20outposts%20were%20to%20be%20established%20%E2%80%98in%20every%20street%2C%20in%20every%20lane%E2%80%99%20in%20which%20volunteers%20would%20be%20based%20who%20would%20maintain%20peace.%20Only%20those%20who%20had%20taken%20a%20pledge%20of%20nonviolence%20were%20to%20serve%20in%20such%20a%20capacity.%20Gandhi%20left%20Bombay%20on%2026%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExtracted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3ENoncooperation%20in%20India%3Cem%3E%20by%20David%20Hardiman%2C%20first%20published%20by%20Context%2C%20an%20imprint%20of%20Westland%20Books.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692070207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15085136%2FCodd-bottle_necks_cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fwhen-a-peaceful-non-cooperation-meeting-in-bombay-turned-violent-leaving-gandhi-distraught%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Troublemakers%20attacked%20Europeans%20and%20even%20Parsis%2C%20Anglo-Indians%20and%20Jews%20whom%20they%20saw%20as%20%E2%80%98loyalists%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Empire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fwhen-a-peaceful-non-cooperation-meeting-in-bombay-turned-violent-leaving-gandhi-distraught%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15084102%2Findia-3639503_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20now%20looks%20all%20but%20certain%20that%20the%20road%20to%202024%20and%20perhaps%20beyond%20is%20going%20to%20be%20paved%20by%20the%20wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People.%20Far%20from%20being%20unidirectional%2C%20this%20anger%20is%20pluralistic%20and%20polysemic%2C%20filtering%20through%20the%20socio-economic%20fabric%20with%20devastating%20consequences%20for%20everyone%20involved%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20tragically%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20those%20who%20have%20to%20live%20with%20this%20memory%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%20For%20a%20republic%2C%20this%20rage%20is%20also%20profoundly%20consequential%20because%20it%20forces%20one%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20nature%20of%20our%20political%20arrangement%2C%20initiate%20a%20rethinking%20of%20accountability%20of%20political%20institutions%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20question%20the%20meanings%20of%20moral%20and%20political%20ideals.%20(For%20some%20examples%20of%20writings%20along%20these%20lines%20in%20light%20of%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3A%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-writes-after-manipur-our-self-serving-morality-8853454%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdouble-engine-the-union-and-state-government-must-answer-for-manipur%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanipur-violence-churachandpur-meitei-kuki-institutionalised-violence%23read-more%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20anger%20also%20brings%20to%20light%20a%20peculiar%20problem%20for%20a%20modern%20constitutional%20democracy.%20What%20happens%20when%20one%20of%20the%20cornerstone%20ideas%20of%20modern%20constitutionalism%20best%20represented%20by%20the%20preambular%20words%20%E2%80%93%20we%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20is%20invoked%20not%20in%20the%20service%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20aspiration%20but%20rather%20as%20a%20vehicle%20for%20a%20people%20who%20are%20wrathful%3F%20Can%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20resist%20a%20sustained%20assault%20from%20forces%20representing%20exclusionary%20visions%20when%20they%20claim%20to%20pursue%20such%20action%20not%20just%20from%20a%20political%20standpoint%20but%2C%20crucially%2C%20from%20a%20constitutional%20standpoint%20of%20speaking%20for%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%3F%20In%20short%2C%20how%20do%20we%20think%20about%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20as%20a%20panacea%20when%20its%20very%20preamble%20is%20used%20to%20undermine%20its%20foundational%20premise%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20collective%20destiny%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20difficult%20questions%20to%20answer%2C%20partly%20because%20constitutionalism%20in%20India%2C%20as%20elsewhere%2C%20has%20always%20been%20as%20much%20a%20political%20project%20as%20it%20has%20been%20a%20normative%20one.%20But%2C%20in%20emphasis%20and%20understanding%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20excessive%20focus%20on%20the%20normative%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20political.%20This%20presents%20at%20least%20two%20problems%20that%20are%20relevant%20to%20the%20contemporary%20crisis.%20Firstly%2C%20this%20belief%20in%20the%20promise%20and%20the%20liberal%20values%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98founding%20document%E2%80%99%20is%20invoked%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20aspirational%20relief%20when%20politics%20fails%20to%20do%20so.%20It%20is%20this%20undying%20faith%20that%20inspired%20people%20to%20come%20out%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20collectively%20read%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20constitution%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20But%2C%20in%20just%20vernacularising%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20raw%20political%20power%20embedded%20in%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20letter%20and%20spirit%20did%20not%20disappear.%20It%20was%20made%20clear%20when%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20the%20state%20stepped%20in%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20these%20protests.%20As%20a%20rights-bearing%20individual%2C%20one%20could%20always%20seek%20remedy%20from%20the%20constitution%2C%20but%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%20has%20the%20state%20given%20up%20its%20all-encompassing%20power.%20If%20anything%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20among%20the%20105%20constitutional%20amendments%20that%20have%20been%20passed%20thus%20far%2C%20with%20a%20rare%20exception%20or%20two%2C%20they%20do%20not%20grant%20or%20extend%20rights%20to%20individuals.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20several%20have%20curtailed%20the%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Indian%20Women%20Fared%20Since%20PM%20Modi%20Invoked%20Nari%20Shakti%20in%20His%20Last%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnarendra-modi-nari-shakti-independence-day%5C%22%3EHow%20Indian%20Women%20Fared%20Since%20PM%20Modi%20Invoked%20Nari%20Shakti%20in%20His%20Last%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20project%20of%20resuscitating%20the%20normative%20ideals%20of%20the%20constitution%20fails%20to%20appropriately%20account%20for%20people%E2%80%99s%20anger.%20In%20just%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20glimpses%20(and%20we%20know%20that%20the%20lived%20experience%20and%20reality%20of%20the%20horrific%20events%20in%20Manipur%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20places%20in%20the%20country%20are%20far%20worse)%20of%20the%20actions%20and%20consequences%20motivated%20by%20sheer%20contempt%2C%20disregard%20and%20the%20unleashing%20of%20the%20wrath%20of%20citizens%20on%20one%20another.%20It%20is%20all%20the%20more%20terrifying%20that%20minorities%20are%20being%20singularly%20and%20systematically%20targeted%20in%20an%20open%2C%20brazen%20manner%20that%20defies%20all%20moral%20norms%20for%20individuals%20and%20the%20community.%20In%20these%20times%2C%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20return%20to%20the%20presumed%20idealism%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Instead%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20if%20constitutionalism%20can%20speak%20to%20the%20visceral%20anger%20of%20the%20survivors%20of%20assaults%20and%20of%20those%20who%20will%20forever%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%20And%2C%20then%2C%20one%20also%20has%20to%20think%20about%20how%20to%20account%20for%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20motivated%20by%20exclusionary%20ideologies%20and%20enabled%20by%20a%20complacent%20state%20that%20often%20looks%20the%20other%20way%20at%20the%20time%20that%20violence%20is%20committed.%20Normative%20resuscitation%20can%20only%20revive%20the%20mythical%20spirit%20of%20the%20constitution.%20It%20cannot%20revive%20the%20body%20weighed%20down%20in%20a%20state%20of%20obedience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20moves%20away%20from%20a%20strictly%20normative%20view%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20one%20finds%20a%20rich%20body%20of%20work%20that%20has%20highlighted%20several%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20constitution%20has%20been%20used%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20not%20used%20appropriately.%20But%20an%20enduring%20theme%20of%20such%20studies%20has%20been%20that%20they%20ultimately%20place%20faith%20in%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20panacea%20for%20socio-political%20ills.%20Undergirding%20the%20document%E2%80%99s%20popular%20roots%2C%20or%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20reflect%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20as%20much%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20govern%20them%2C%20and%20arguing%20that%20the%20courts%20could%20in%20the%20ultimate%20regard%20serve%20as%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20republic%20even%20as%20all%20other%20established%20political%20institutions%20and%20mechanisms%20fail%2C%20while%20helpful%20in%20limited%20ways%2C%20nevertheless%20only%20serves%20to%20place%20the%20constitution%20on%20a%20pedestal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20one%20values%20these%20approaches%20for%20their%20obvious%20democratising%2C%20ameliorating%20and%20progressive%20impulses%20in%20limited%20ways%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20they%20fail%20to%20see%20the%20rising%20danger%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20constitution%20from%20within%20rather%20than%20without.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20preambular%20invocation%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%20could%20in%20its%20own%20way%20become%20the%20ultimate%20instrument%20through%20which%20the%20edifice%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20limited%20emancipatory%20potential%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20undone.%20Saving%20the%20constitution%20from%20a%20wrathful%20people%2C%20then%2C%20becomes%20an%20urgent%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20rescue%20the%20constitution%2C%20ironically%2C%20is%20to%20lessen%20moral%20expectations%20from%20the%20document.%20There%20is%20a%20compelling%20need%20to%20do%20so%2C%20for%20otherwise%2C%20one%20is%20constantly%20forced%20to%20reinvigorate%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20document%2C%20which%20for%20the%20most%20part%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20historical%20archives%20but%20rather%20in%20carefully%20constructed%20inductive%20and%20deductive%20reasoning%20by%20scholars%20and%20likeminded%20public%20thinkers.%20%C2%A0The%20constitution%20carries%20an%20undue%20moral%20burden%20to%20speak%20to%20situations%20that%20have%20already%20far%20exceeded%20the%20context%20in%20which%20the%20document%20was%20written.%20In%20a%20proverbial%20sense%2C%20then%2C%20the%20emperor%20may%20not%20be%20naked%20but%20is%20not%20fully%20clothed%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20not%20a%20call%20for%20nihilism%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20constitution.%20Neither%20is%20it%20an%20argument%20for%20undoing%20the%20limited%20goods%20that%20a%20constitution%20does%20provide%20and%20has%20provided%20for%20millions%20since%20independence.%20Rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20call%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20constitution%20by%20remembering%20two%20precepts%3A%20First%2C%20recognise%20that%20a%20self-sustaining%20normative%20value%20of%20the%20constitution%20does%20not%20exist.%20It%20is%20a%20chimera.%20The%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20and%20has%20always%20been%20about%20protection%20and%20sharing%20of%20state%20power%2C%20not%20a%20noble%20document%20that%20exists%20to%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20citizens.%20It%20would%20be%20better%20to%20consider%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20political%20and%20not%20a%20normative%20document.%20Several%20scholars%20have%20already%20made%20this%20important%20shift%20in%20their%20research%20on%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20Second%2C%20there%20are%20important%20lessons%20in%20Indian%20constitutional%20history%20that%20can%20provide%20a%20tentative%20pathway%20to%20effectively%20rethink%20the%20role%20that%20the%20constitution%20can%20play%20in%20the%20socio-political%20imaginaries.%20Politics%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20here%20too.%20It%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20briefly%20expand%20on%20this%20latter%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20striking%20features%20of%20constitutional%20developments%20in%20the%20early%20to%20mid-20th%20century%20is%20the%20well-known%20colonial%20context.%20Strangely%2C%20though%20written%20about%2C%20it%20is%20relatively%20under-appreciated%20in%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20constitutionalism%20in%20India.%20A%20defining%20trait%20of%20this%20context%20was%20that%20even%20as%20Britain%20wrote%20constitutional%20legislation%20for%20India%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20ultimately%20defending%20the%20project%20of%20colonialism%2C%20in%20its%20impact%20and%20implementation%20it%20offered%20ways%20to%20Indian%20nationalist%20leaders%20to%20claim%20part-ownership%20of%20governance%20and%20aspire%20for%20imagining%20complete%20autonomy.%20This%20meant%20that%20despite%20their%20best%20efforts%20to%20uniformly%20translate%20the%20political%20project%20of%20colonialism%20into%20a%20constitutional%20language%2C%20the%20endeavour%20did%20not%20succeed%20entirely.%20Likewise%2C%20for%20the%20anticolonial%20nationalists%2C%20the%20language%20of%20constitutionalism%20forced%20the%20language%20of%20representation%2C%20which%20offered%20an%20opportunity%20for%20different%20regional%20and%20national%20interests%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20own%20voices.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20process%20never%20allowed%20for%20a%20way%20to%20translate%20the%20mythical%20idea%20of%20national%20unity%20into%20a%20constitutional%20project.%20Constitutionalism%2C%20by%20its%20very%20nature%20and%20because%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20competing%20political%20interests%2C%20prevented%20the%20hegemony%20of%20a%20single%20representative%20group.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20for%20leaders%20of%20both%20colonialism%20and%20nationalism%2C%20constitutionalism%20never%20emerged%20as%20a%20faithful%20ally%20for%20their%20respective%20political%20projects.%20The%20relationship%20between%20them%20was%20always%20tension-prone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi's%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20the%20productivity%20of%20this%20tension%20that%20helped%20different%20interested%20groups%20to%20stake%20a%20claim%20in%20the%20making%20of%20the%20constitution.%20For%20instance%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20rigorous%20defence%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20Dalits%20and%20M.A.%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20stance%20on%20Pakistan%20had%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20constitutional%20space%20that%20opened%20up%20in%20the%20colonial%20context.%20Likewise%2C%20others%20such%20as%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20princely%20states%20similarly%20put%20forward%20their%20constitutional%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20an%20important%20lesson%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20this%20highly%20abbreviated%20account%20of%20Indian%20constitutional%20history%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20the%20story%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20one%20of%20securing%20state%20power%2C%20and%20the%20colonial%20context%20enabled%20the%20proliferation%20of%20different%20political%20interests%2C%20each%20making%20their%20own%20claims%20on%20such%20power.%20In%20the%20postcolonial%20context%2C%20with%20the%20establishment%20and%20entrenchment%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20opportunity%20provided%20by%20the%20colonial%20context%20disappeared%2C%20leading%20the%20different%20politically%20organised%20groups%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20language%20of%20nationalism%20or%20risk%20being%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20then%2C%20constitutionalism%20is%20often%20strongest%20when%20there%20are%20multiple%20competing%20political%20interests.%20It%20is%20compromised%20when%20there%20is%20a%20singular%2C%20strong%20political%20force%20dominant%20in%20the%20country.%20If%20constitutionalism%20is%20to%20regain%20its%20strength%2C%20then%20the%20solution%20may%20not%20be%20to%20look%20to%20the%20constitution%20from%20an%20apolitical%20or%20normative%20point%20of%20view%20but%20rather%20to%20understand%20and%20engage%20with%20its%20fundamentally%20political%20character.%20This%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20not%20only%20save%20the%20people%20from%20the%20constitution%20but%20importantly%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20constitution%20from%20the%20wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArvind%20Elangovan%20is%20Professor%20of%20History%20and%20Associate%20Chair%2C%20School%20of%20Humanities%20and%20Cultural%20Studies%2C%20College%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%2C%20Wright%20State%20University%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692069121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15084102%2Findia-3639503_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20preambular%20invocation%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%20could%20in%20its%20own%20way%20become%20the%20ultimate%20instrument%20through%20which%20the%20edifice%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20limited%20emancipatory%20potential%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20undone.%20Saving%20the%20constitution%20from%20a%20wrathful%20people%2C%20then%2C%20becomes%20an%20urgent%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Indicted%20in%20Georgia%20on%202020%20Election%20Interference%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692068777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FGettyImages-1579471628-e1691435010223.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235689744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Fulton%20County%20grand%20jury%20has%20indicted%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20several%20allies%20on%20Monday%20over%20his%20alleged%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%20in%20Georgia.%20This%20is%20the%20fourth%20criminal%20case%20to%20be%20brought%20against%20the%20former%20president.%20Fulton%20County%20district%20attorney%20Fanis%20Willis%20kicked%20off%20the%20investigation%20after%20a%20leaked%20phone%20call%20between%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22McKinley%20Franklin%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fdonald-trump-indicted-georgia-2020-election-interference-1235689744%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fdonald-trump-indicted-georgia-2020-election-interference-1235689744%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fdonald-trump-indicted-georgia-2020-election-interference-1235689744%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drug-coated%20balloon%20gives%20new%20life%20to%20Bengaluru%20man%20who%20had%20over%20100%20strokes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692067331000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102745923%2Cimgsize-62830.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fdrug-coated-balloon-gives-new-life-to-man-who-had-over-100-strokes%2Farticleshow%2F102737413.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohan%20had%20severe%20narrowing%20of%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20brain%20due%20to%20inflammation%20in%20one%20of%20his%20arteries.%20Such%20patients%20are%20usually%20advised%20to%20take%20steroids%20and%20blood%20thinners%20until%20the%20symptoms%20subside.%20But%20he%20was%20not%20responding%20to%20any%20drugs%2Finjections.%20He%20would%20have%20multiple%20strokes%20daily.%20MRIs%20done%20in%20multiple%20centres%20showed%20the%20strokes%20had%20caused%20damage%20to%20his%20brain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MINI%20THOMAS%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fdrug-coated-balloon-gives-new-life-to-man-who-had-over-100-strokes%2Farticleshow%2F102737413.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi's%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Manipur%20to%20Mewat%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20new%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20portray%20a%20pretty%20picture.%20It%20is%20a%20holy%20mess.%20The%20shift%20in%20nomenclature%20from%20Amrit%20Kaal%20(auspicious%20period)%20to%20Kartavya%20Kaal%20(period%20of%20duty)%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20a%20complete%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20political%20leadership.%20It%20has%20hampered%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20which%20have%20consequently%20failed%20to%20bring%20the%20violence%20under%20control.%20But%20this%20is%20no%20ordinary%20violence%20of%20a%20communal%20riot%20or%20a%20socio-economic%20protest%20that%20independent%20India%20has%20been%20witness%20to%20many%20a%20time%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20decades%20of%20its%20existence.%20It%20is%20not%20even%20an%20insurgency%20like%20Kashmir%20or%20Punjab%20or%20Nagaland%20or%20Mizoram.%20The%20violence%20is%20not%20due%20to%20criminal%20gangs%20shooting%20each%20other%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai.%20These%20are%20not%20misguided%20youth%20taking%20up%20guns%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20communist%20revolution.%20This%20is%20different%3A%20violence%20with%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20mobs.%20Mobs%2C%20who%20have%20been%20empowered%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20political%20leadership%20is%20not%20simply%20condoning%20their%20action%20or%20looking%20away%3B%20it%20is%20using%20these%20mobs%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20State%20against%20a%20minority%20community.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20majoritarian%20Meitei%20mobs%20are%20enabled%20by%20allowing%20ransacking%20of%20lethal%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20police%20armouries.%20The%20proof%20lies%20in%20the%20bewildering%20fact%20that%20not%20a%20single%20miscreant%20was%20caught%20or%20shot%20by%20the%20cops%20as%20these%20armouries%20were%20supposedly%20being%20looted.%20Call%20it%20connivance%20or%20collusion%20or%20co-option%2C%20or%20all%20of%20the%20above%2C%20the%20mobs%20are%20the%20masters%20of%20this%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20control%20them%3B%20they%20control%20the%20state%20and%20are%20aware%20of%20their%20power.%20Invariably%2C%20these%20mobs%20belong%20to%20the%20majority%20community%20and%20are%20politically%20from%20the%20same%20parivar%20as%20the%20party%20ruling%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre.%20It%20is%20the%20reason%20they%20are%20empowered%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Their%20public%20acceptance%20as%20custodians%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20popular%20culture%20and%20public%20morality%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20mandate%2C%20except%20their%20brute%20power%20to%20inflict%20violence.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20incorrect%20to%20see%20them%20as%20adherents%20of%20VD%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20dictum%2C%20as%20cited%20by%20Prof%20Vinayak%20Chaturvedi%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20understand%20themselves%20as%20Hindus%20through%20acts%20of%20violence%E2%80%9D.%20The%20danger%20lies%20in%20these%20mobs%20trying%20to%20ensure%20what%20Savarkar%20desired%20of%20Hindus%3A%20they%20%E2%80%9Cneeded%20to%20embrace%20permanent%20war%20as%20part%20of%20their%20future%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20RPF%20cop%20Chetan%20Singh%20identifies%2C%20selects%20and%20kills%20Muslims%2C%20that%20future%20seems%20to%20be%20upon%20us%20now.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20lone%20wolf%20but%20the%20representative%20of%20an%20empowered%20mob.%20The%20lines%20between%20the%20mob%20and%20cops%20have%20blurred.%20In%20both%20Manipur%20and%20Mewat%2C%20this%20mob%20is%20indistinguishable%20from%20the%20cops.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20reports%20show%20the%20two%20working%20in%20tandem%2C%20jointly%20targeting%20the%20minority%20community.%20In%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20poor%2C%20marginalised%2C%20and%20subordinated%20sometimes%20resort%20to%20violence%2C%20often%20genocidal%20in%20nature%20%E2%80%93%20at%20times%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20state%2C%20in%20other%20instances%20independent%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20order%20to%20stake%20a%20claim%20within%E2%80%A6to%20make%20history%20as%20killers%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Hindutva%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmpowering%20the%20violent%20and%20hateful%20mob%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20strengthen%20the%20Indian%20State.%20It%20weakens%20and%20hollows%20it%20out.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20state%20has%20simply%20ceased%20to%20exist.%20In%20Mewat%2C%20the%20state%20has%20no%20credibility%20left.%20Few%20trust%20it%20anymore%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20epithet%20BJP%20used%20to%20unleash%20on%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20It%20is%20a%20disempowered%20state%2C%20where%20the%20mob%20has%20been%20empowered%20at%20its%20cost.%20This%20disempowerment%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20remain%20limited%20to%20one%20aspect%20or%20geography.%20Slowly%20but%20surely%2C%20it%20encroaches%20on%20to%20other%20domains%20and%20areas%2C%20sapping%20the%20state%20of%20its%20energies%20to%20accomplish%20even%20the%20minimum%20obligatory%20tasks.%20We%20need%20look%20no%20further%20than%20Pakistan%20to%20see%20where%20this%20path%20leads%20to.%20It%20is%20surprising%20that%20those%20who%20imagine%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Pakistan%E2%80%9D%20can%20be%20so%20blind%20to%20the%20eventual%20destination%20of%20their%20desired%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20disempowered%20state%2C%20flailing%20and%20fouling%2C%20is%20doomed%20for%20disaster.%20Vigilantism%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20this%20journey.%20We%20have%20witnessed%20it%20enough%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cow%20protection%20or%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99.%20In%20no%20other%20modern%20civilised%20society%20have%20so%20many%20men%20been%20publicly%20lynched%20as%20have%20been%20in%20India%20by%20Hindutva%20vigilante%20groups.%20The%20vigilantism%20of%20the%20cops%20is%20well%20known%2C%20but%20that%20crossed%20a%20limit%20in%20Gujarat%20when%20the%20state%20police%20publicly%20flogged%20young%20Muslims%20and%20made%20a%20video%20of%20it.%20Even%20the%20Taliban%20regime%20in%20Afghanistan%20claimed%20a%20moral%20high%20ground%20over%20Gujarat%20Police%20after%20that%20video!%20Gujarat%20has%20seen%20unbroken%20BJP%20rule%20this%20century%2C%20and%20makes%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20top%20political%2C%20bureaucratic%20and%20business%20leadership%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20It%20was%20sold%20as%20the%20model%20state%20in%202014%2C%20which%20many%20gullible%20Indians%20fell%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20gaze%20into%20the%20abyss%2C%20the%20abyss%20gazes%20also%20into%20you.%E2%80%9D%20Nietzsche%20may%20have%20meant%20it%20differently%20but%20when%20a%20state%20gazes%20adoringly%20into%20the%20abyss%20of%20a%20mob%2C%20it%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20becoming%20the%20mob.%20The%20use%20of%20bulldozers%20to%20target%20residential%20and%20commercial%20properties%20of%20Muslims%2C%20ostensibly%20for%20violation%20of%20municipal%20rules%2C%20is%20vigilantism%20by%20the%20state.%20It%20breeds%20misery%20and%20hate.%20It%20destroys%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20sounds%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20our%20constitutional%20order.%20The%20state%20has%20turned%20into%20an%20unjust%20monster%2C%20trying%20to%20impose%20a%20new%20moral%20order%20%E2%80%93%20an%20immoral%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mutation%20had%20no%20place%20in%20the%20India%20that%20was%20imagined%20in%20the%20crucible%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20shaped%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20The%20bulldozer%20is%20the%20symbol%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20new%20India.%20It%20is%20the%20icon%20of%20vigilantism%20and%20mob%20empowerment.%20It%20is%20the%20withering%20away%20of%20the%20tate%20through%20deliberate%20disempowerment.%20A%20disempowered%20state%20can%20be%20the%20stepfather%20of%20despotism%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%20It%20can%20be%20majoritarian%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20democratic.%20It%20can%20be%20new%20India%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20our%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fempowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state-2645701%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2F%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692066602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20no%20other%20modern%20civilised%20society%20have%20so%20many%20men%20been%20publicly%20lynched%20as%20have%20been%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Car%20thief%20uses%20police%20portal%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20owners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692065910000%2C%22visual%22%