nnium-city%20architectural%20sheen%20is%20built%20upon%20the%20labour%20and%20sweat%20of%20Bengali%20Muslim%20migrant%20labourers%20and%20construction%20workers%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20those%20who%20were%20beaten%20up%20and%20forced%20to%20evict%20on%20the%20accusation%20of%20being%20Bangladeshis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20persistent%20othering%20narrative%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20has%20festered%20a%20disease%20of%20hatred%2C%20fomenting%20a%20series%20of%20Islamophobic%20propaganda%20and%20fanning%20brazen%20violence%20sabotaging%20the%20minority%20community%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20education%2C%20means%20of%20livelihood%2C%20healthcare%2C%20safety%20and%20dignity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20increasing%20mob-ification%20of%20the%20vigilante%20outfits%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20has%20also%20been%20polarising%20women%20in%20terms%20of%20identity.%20A%20patriarchal%2C%20hyper-masculine%20and%20muscle-flexing%20state%20is%20increasingly%20dismantling%20women%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20rights%2C%20especially%20those%20demanding%20justice%20and%20those%20bearing%20marginalised%20identities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20daughters%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20Indians%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20Twitter%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape%20erupted%20in%20rage%20at%20a%20video%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20naked%20parading%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%20amidst%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20has%20seen%20women%20being%20raped%2C%20their%20bodies%20brutalised%20with%20reports%20noted%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20%E2%80%9Chanded%20over%E2%80%9D%20to%20armed%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%202023%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20of%20Manipur%20has%20put%201