onomy%2C%20the%20assault%20on%20their%20identity%2C%20their%20dignity%20and%20their%20health%3F%20Why%20is%20it%20that%20only%20when%20Indian%20men%20feel%20ashamed%20or%20outraged%20that%20the%20nation%20must%20rise%20from%20its%20apolitical%20slumber%3F%C2%A0%20Who%20decides%20who%20deserves%20justice%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWrestlers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20same%20year%2C%20Olympic%20and%20Worlds%20medal-winning%20women%20wrestlers%20protesting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20were%20forcibly%20removed%20and%20allegedly%20attacked%20by%20police.%20They%20were%20protesting%20against%20police%20inaction%20against%20outgoing%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20and%20BJP%20MP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprofile-on-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh%2Farticle66928654.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20the%20female%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20wrestlers%20including%20heavyweights%20like%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20are%20otherwise%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20ki%20Beti%E2%80%9D%20upon%20winning%20medals%20and%20bringing%20laurels%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20were%20accused%20of%20having%20political%20agenda%20in%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20workplace%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20a%20raging%20issue%20of%20our%20time%2C%20was%20trivialised%20and%20the%20powerful%20wrestlers%20were%20rendered%20defenceless%20against%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20predator%2C%20the%2066-year-old%20Singh.%20Malik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20seven%20days%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20sexual%20harasser%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20and%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20take%20seven%20hours%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20us%20for%20peacefully%20protesting%20%5Bduring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tweeted.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20country%20under%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edictatorship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20The%20whole%20world%20is%20watching%20how%20the%20government%20is%20treating%20its%20players.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20remarked%20that%20this%20is%20indeed%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F5%2F28%2Fworld-is-watching-indian-police-drag-away-protesting-wrestlers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eculture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20WFI.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20head%20himself%20is%20like%20that%2C%20what%20action%20will%20he%20take%20against%20others%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20on%20August%2011%2C%202023%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said%20that%20there%20is%20enough%20evidence%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprofile-on-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh%2Farticle66928654.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20him%20to%20be%20put%20on%20trial%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdelhi-court-brij-bhushan%2Farticle67107090.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esexual%20harassment%20case%20filed%20by%20women%20wrestlers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20had%20filed%20a%201%2C000-page%20chargesheet%20on%20June%2015%20against%20the%20accused%20for%20offences%20under%20Sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20and%20354D%20(stalking)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20Police%20have%20not%20opposed%20his%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EC.K.%20Raulji%2C