ion%20of%20girls%20their%20right%20to%20education%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20upheld%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20state%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20suggested%20that%20government%20colleges%20with%20uniform%20codes%20are%20well%20within%20their%20rights%20to%20put%20a%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20restriction%E2%80%9D%20on%20Muslim%20female%20students%20wearing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijabs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20Muslim%20girls%20were%20barred%20from%20taking%20examinations%20and%20several%20found%20their%20bodily%20autonomy%20threatened%20and%20violated%20as%20invigilators%20and%20institutional%20gatekeepers%20instructed%20them%20to%20take%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20off%20before%20entering%20the%20educational%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20stated%20that%20the%20total%20dropouts%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E-wearing%20girls%20stand%20at%201%2C010%20because%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ban%20(or%20other%20reasons%20as%20well)%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fhijab-ban-one-year-on-muslim-students-in-karnataka-continue-their-fight-for-education-news-267990%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPUCL%20fact-finding%20report%20released%20in%20September%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20the%20Modi-led%20NDA%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20prided%20itself%20on%20its%20noble%20mission%20of%20liberating%20Muslim%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esisters%20and%20daughters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20tyranny%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhijab-ban-narendra-modi-muslim-women-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cspan