t%20special%20%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Child%E2%80%99%2C%20Navin%20narrates%20a%20hilarious%20story%20from%20his%20childhood%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20chawl%20in%20Golibar%20road.%20In%20this%20particular%20segment%2C%20he%20recalled%20how%20there%20were%20just%20five%20common%20toilets%20for%20hundreds%20of%20families%20living%20in%20his%20chawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20one%20morning%20as%20a%20five-year-old%2C%20Navin%20stepped%20out%20with%20a%20bucket%20of%20water%20and%20walked%20towards%20the%20common%20toilet%20stalls%20to%20do%20his%20business.%20Unable%20to%20control%20his%20bowels%2C%20however%2C%20he%20released%20portions%20of%20his%20excrement%20along%20the%20passageway.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20collection%20of%2010%20neighbourhood%20aunties%20stood%20outside%20his%20home%20complaining%20to%20his%20mother%20about%20what%20he%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hilariously%20denying%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tells%20him%20something%20that%20he%20would%20hear%20again%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(do%20whatever%20you%20want%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20your%20private%20space%2C%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20outside)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20he%20finally%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20come%20out%20and%20introduce%20his%20partner%20to%20his%20mother%20at%2027%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20his%20queer%20identity%2C%20but%20did%20say%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20and%20it%20was%20Pride%20Month%20in%20Mumbai.%20Navin%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20photographed%20kissing%20each%20other%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E