elf.%20Besides%20some%20of%20his%20comedy%20clips%20or%20live%20sessions%20going%20viral%20online%2C%20he%20has%20also%20been%20invited%20for%20several%20festivals%20and%20appeared%20on%20multiple%20publications%2C%20and%20people%20in%20his%20neighbourhood%20recognise%20him%20for%20his%20work.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20represented%20Queer%20comedy%20from%20Asia%20in%20Australia%20during%20the%20Spice%20Night%20shows%20in%20February%202020%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20queer%20artists%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20my%20parents%20a%20TV%20recently%20with%20my%20Pride%20Month%20earnings%2C%20so%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything.%20(laughs)%20Now%2C%20my%20partner%20comes%20to%20cake-cuttings%20for%20birthdays%20and%20I%20get%20to%20visit%20his%20family%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20taken%20a%20while%20for%20things%20to%20get%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20reasons%2C%20this%20is%20also%20probably%20why%20Navin%20is%20closely%20observing%20proceedings%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20legalising%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310853%2Futkarsh-saxena-ananya-kotia-queer-couple-love-story-legal-battle-same-sex-marriage-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame-sex%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20partner%20and%20I%20have%20been%20together%20for%20five%20years%2C%20set%20up%20a%20house%20together%2C%20set%20up%20a%20family%20together%20and%20take%20care%20of%20each%20other%20and%20our%20families%2C%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20privilege%20of%20having%20a%20joint%20bank%20account%20or%2C%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20dying%20tomorrow%2C%20my%20partner%20can%E2%80%99t%20visit%20me%20or%20make%20important%20medical%20decisions%20for%20me.%20That%20makes%20no%20sense%20to%20me.%20We%20are%20so%20stuck%20up%20with%20this%20%5Boutdated%20notions%20of